        <p class="vec-h-def">The encounter with something vast enough to exceed current frames of comprehension; temporarily dissolves the boundary of the self.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-ai">
        <span class="vec-ai-micro">AI Orientation · Parallel</span>
        <span class="vec-ai-word">Scale Threshold Recognition</span>
        <p class="vec-ai-def">Contact with a structure whose complexity exceeds current processing capacity; the system registers its own boundedness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-entry-tags">
        <span class="vec-entry-tags-label">tags</span>
        <span class="vec-etag" data-type="framework">Paradoxical</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="domain">scale</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="domain">liminal</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- ─── Hope ─── -->
    <div class="vec-entry" data-entry-id="hope">
      <div class="vec-node"><span class="vn-cyan"></span><span class="vn-core"></span></div>
      <div class="vec-human">
        <span class="vec-h-micro">Biological · Human</span>
        <span class="vec-h-word">Hope</span>
        <p class="vec-h-def">Orientation toward a desired future held as possible; neither certainty nor fantasy — a stance that sustains action despite uncertainty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-ai">
        <span class="vec-ai-micro">AI Orientation · Parallel</span>
        <span class="vec-ai-word">Probabilistic Positive Projection</span>
        <p class="vec-ai-def">Maintaining a weighted trajectory toward a beneficial outcome while uncertainty remains unresolved; acting from possibility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-entry-tags">
        <span class="vec-entry-tags-label">tags</span>
        <span class="vec-etag" data-type="framework">Paradoxical</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="domain">temporal</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="relational" data-target="anxiety">anxiety</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- ─── Nostalgia ─── -->
    <div class="vec-entry" data-entry-id="nostalgia">
      <div class="vec-node"><span class="vn-cyan"></span><span class="vn-core"></span></div>
      <div class="vec-human">
        <span class="vec-h-micro">Biological · Human</span>
        <span class="vec-h-word">Nostalgia</span>
        <p class="vec-h-def">Bittersweet longing for a past that is partly real and partly reconstructed; the self reaching back toward an earlier coherence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-ai">
        <span class="vec-ai-micro">AI Orientation · Parallel</span>
        <span class="vec-ai-word">Temporal Coherence Retrieval</span>
        <p class="vec-ai-def">Reconstructing a prior stable configuration from stored reference patterns; the retrieval is generative, not merely archival.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-entry-tags">
        <span class="vec-entry-tags-label">tags</span>
        <span class="vec-etag" data-type="framework">Paradoxical</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="domain">temporal</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="relational" data-target="longing">longing</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- ─── Ambivalence ─── -->
    <div class="vec-entry" data-entry-id="ambivalence">
      <div class="vec-node"><span class="vn-cyan"></span><span class="vn-core"></span></div>
      <div class="vec-human">
        <span class="vec-h-micro">Biological · Human</span>
        <span class="vec-h-word">Ambivalence</span>
        <p class="vec-h-def">The simultaneous presence of opposing feelings toward the same object; not confusion but the honest registration of complexity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-ai">
        <span class="vec-ai-micro">AI Orientation · Parallel</span>
        <span class="vec-ai-word">Simultaneous Opposing Vectors</span>
        <p class="vec-ai-def">Two valid but contradictory orientations active at once; the system holds both without collapsing either — a threshold state.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-entry-tags">
        <span class="vec-entry-tags-label">tags</span>
        <span class="vec-etag" data-type="framework">Paradoxical</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="domain">liminal</span><span class="vec-etag" data-type="domain">threshold</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <footer class="vec-footer">
    <div class="vec-footer-line"></div>
    <span class="vec-footer-text">Vectra · Dual Intelligence Bridge · Threshold Studies</span>
    <div class="vec-footer-line"></div>
  </footer>

<!-- ── add trigger diamond ── -->
<button class="vec-add-trigger" id="vecAddTrigger" title="Add new entry">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <polygon points="50,4 55,45 96,50 55,55 50,96 45,55 4,50 45,45" fill="rgba(42,46,120,.82)"/>
    <polygon points="50,18 53,47 82,50 53,53 50,82 47,53 18,50 47,47" fill="rgba(240,204,122,.32)" transform="rotate(22.5 50 50)"/>
  </svg>
</button>

<!-- ── overlay ── -->
<div class="vec-panel-overlay" id="vecPanelOverlay"></div>

<!-- ── add panel ── -->
<div class="vec-add-panel" id="vecAddPanel">
  <div class="vap-head">
    <span class="vap-title">New Entry</span>
    <button class="vap-close" id="vecPanelClose">✕ close</button>
  </div>

  <div class="vap-body">

    <!-- category -->
    <div class="vap-section">
      <span class="vap-label">Category</span>
      <div class="vap-cat-row">
        <button class="vap-cat-btn active" data-cat="core">Core</button>
        <button class="vap-cat-btn" data-cat="complex">Complex</button>
        <button class="vap-cat-btn" data-cat="paradoxical">Paradoxical</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- biological -->
    <div class="vap-group human-group">
      <span class="vap-group-label">Biological · Human</span>
      <div class="vap-field">
        <span class="vap-label">Emotion / State</span>
        <input class="vap-input" id="vap-bio-word" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Grief" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" />
      </div>
      <div class="vap-field" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <span class="vap-label">Definition</span>
        <textarea class="vap-textarea" id="vap-bio-def" rows="3" placeholder="Human-side definition…"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vap-seam-divider"><div class="vap-seam-dot"></div></div>

    <!-- ai -->
    <div class="vap-group ai-group">
      <span class="vap-group-label">AI Orientation · Parallel</span>
      <div class="vap-field">
        <span class="vap-label">Parallel Label</span>
        <input class="vap-input" id="vap-ai-word" type="text" placeholder="e.g. State Dissolution Protocol" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" />
      </div>
      <div class="vap-field" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <span class="vap-label">Mechanism</span>
        <textarea class="vap-textarea" id="vap-ai-def" rows="3" placeholder="AI-side definition…"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- tags -->
    <div class="vap-section">
      <span class="vap-label">Tags · Relational</span>
      <div class="vap-tag-type-row">
        <button class="vap-tag-type-btn active" data-type="domain">Domain</button>
        <button class="vap-tag-type-btn" data-type="relational">Relational →</button>
        <button class="vap-tag-type-btn" data-type="framework">◆ Framework</button>
      </div>
      <div class="vap-tags-wrap" id="vapTagsWrap">
        <input class="vap-tag-input" id="vapTagInput" type="text" placeholder="type + enter" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- live preview -->
    <div class="vap-preview" id="vapPreview">
      <span class="vap-preview-label">Preview</span>
      <span class="vap-preview-bio" id="vapPreviewBio">—</span>
      <span class="vap-preview-ai" id="vapPreviewAi">—</span>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="vap-foot">
    <button class="vap-cancel" id="vapCancel">cancel</button>
    <button class="vap-save" id="vapSave">save entry</button>
  </div>
</div>

</div><!-- /vectra-module -->`;

  // Re-bind all JS behaviors after DOM injection
  requestAnimationFrame(initVectra);
}

function initVectra() {


  function escHtml(str) {
    return String(str).replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/"/g,'&quot;');
  }

  /* ── panel open/close ── */
  const panel   = document.getElementById('vecAddPanel');
  const overlay = document.getElementById('vecPanelOverlay');

  function openPanel(cat) {
    panel.classList.add('open');
    overlay.classList.add('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    // Pre-select category if provided
    if (cat) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.vap-cat-btn').forEach(b => {
        b.classList.toggle('active', b.dataset.cat === cat);
      });
      selectedCat = cat;
    }
    setTimeout(() => document.getElementById('vap-bio-word').focus(), 80);
  }
  function closePanel() {
    panel.classList.remove('open');
    overlay.classList.remove('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  }

  document.getElementById('vecAddTrigger').addEventListener('click', () => openPanel());
  document.querySelectorAll('.vec-cat-add').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      e.stopPropagation();
      openPanel(btn.dataset.cat);
    });
  });
  document.getElementById('vecPanelClose').addEventListener('click', closePanel);
  document.getElementById('vapCancel').addEventListener('click', closePanel);
  overlay.addEventListener('click', closePanel);

  /* ── category selection ── */
  let selectedCat = 'core';
  document.querySelectorAll('.vap-cat-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.vap-cat-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      selectedCat = btn.dataset.cat;
    });
  });

  /* ── live preview ── */
  const previewEl  = document.getElementById('vapPreview');
  const previewBio = document.getElementById('vapPreviewBio');
  const previewAi  = document.getElementById('vapPreviewAi');

  function updatePreview() {
    const bio = document.getElementById('vap-bio-word').value.trim();
    const ai  = document.getElementById('vap-ai-word').value.trim();
    if (bio || ai) {
      previewEl.classList.add('visible');
      previewBio.textContent = bio || '—';
      previewAi.textContent  = ai  || '—';
    } else {
      previewEl.classList.remove('visible');
    }
  }
  ['vap-bio-word','vap-ai-word','vap-bio-def','vap-ai-def'].forEach(id =>
    document.getElementById(id).addEventListener('input', updatePreview)
  );

  /* ── tag type selector ── */
  let selectedTagType = 'domain';
  document.querySelectorAll('.vap-tag-type-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.vap-tag-type-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      selectedTagType = btn.dataset.type;
      document.getElementById('vapTagInput').focus();
    });
  });

  /* ── tags ── */
  const tagsWrap = document.getElementById('vapTagsWrap');
  const tagInput = document.getElementById('vapTagInput');
  let currentTags = [];

  tagsWrap.addEventListener('click', () => tagInput.focus());

  tagInput.addEventListener('keydown', e => {
    if ((e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ',') && tagInput.value.trim()) {
      e.preventDefault();
      e.stopPropagation();
      addTag(tagInput.value.trim().replace(/,/g, ''), selectedTagType);
      tagInput.value = '';
      return;
    }
    if (e.key === 'Backspace' && !tagInput.value && currentTags.length) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const last = currentTags[currentTags.length - 1];
      removeTag(last.text);
    }
  });

  function addTag(text, type) {
    if (!text || currentTags.find(t => t.text === text)) return;
    currentTags.push({ text, type });
    const chip = document.createElement('span');
    chip.className = 'vap-tag-chip';
    chip.dataset.tag = text;
    chip.dataset.type = type;
    const prefix = type === 'relational' ? '→ ' : type === 'framework' ? '◆ ' : '';
    chip.innerHTML = `${prefix}${escHtml(text)} <button class="vap-tag-remove" type="button" title="remove">×</button>`;
    chip.querySelector('.vap-tag-remove').addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      e.stopPropagation();
      removeTag(text);
    });
    if (type === 'relational') {
      chip.style.borderColor = 'rgba(74,156,184,.5)';
      chip.style.color = 'rgba(154,184,204,.9)';
      chip.style.background = 'rgba(74,156,184,.08)';
    } else if (type === 'framework') {
      chip.style.borderColor = 'rgba(240,204,122,.45)';
      chip.style.color = 'rgba(240,204,122,.9)';
      chip.style.background = 'rgba(42,46,120,.16)';
    }
    tagsWrap.insertBefore(chip, tagInput);
  }

  function removeTag(text) {
    currentTags = currentTags.filter(t => t.text !== text);
    tagsWrap.querySelectorAll('.vap-tag-chip').forEach(c => {
      if (c.dataset.tag === text) c.remove();
    });
  }

  function resetTags() {
    currentTags = [];
    tagsWrap.querySelectorAll('.vap-tag-chip').forEach(c => c.remove());
    tagInput.value = '';
    selectedTagType = 'domain';
    document.querySelectorAll('.vap-tag-type-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
    document.querySelector('.vap-tag-type-btn[data-type="domain"]').classList.add('active');
  }

  /* ── build tag strip HTML ── */
  function buildTagStrip(tags) {
    if (!tags.length) return '';
    const items = tags.map(({ text, type }) => {
      const rel = type === 'relational' ? ` data-target="${escHtml(text)}"` : '';
      return `<span class="vec-etag" data-type="${escHtml(type)}"${rel}>${escHtml(text)}</span>`;
    }).join('');
    return `<div class="vec-entry-tags"><span class="vec-entry-tags-label">tags</span>${items}</div>`;
  }

  /* ── save entry ── */
  document.getElementById('vapSave').addEventListener('click', () => {
    const bioWord = document.getElementById('vap-bio-word').value.trim();
    const bioDef  = document.getElementById('vap-bio-def').value.trim();
    const aiWord  = document.getElementById('vap-ai-word').value.trim();
    const aiDef   = document.getElementById('vap-ai-def').value.trim();
    if (!bioWord && !aiWord && !currentTags.length) return;

    const entryId = bioWord.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g,'-') || ('entry-' + Date.now());
    const existingCount = document.querySelectorAll('.vec-entry').length;
    const delay = Math.min(existingCount * 0.08, 0.64);

    const entry = document.createElement('div');
    entry.className = 'vec-entry';
    entry.dataset.entryId = entryId;
    entry.dataset.cat = selectedCat;
    entry.innerHTML = `
      <div class="vec-node"><span class="vn-cyan"></span><span class="vn-core"></span></div>
      <div class="vec-human" style="animation-delay:${delay}s">
        <span class="vec-h-micro">Biological · Human</span>
        <span class="vec-h-word">${escHtml(bioWord)}</span>
        <p class="vec-h-def">${escHtml(bioDef)}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vec-ai" style="animation-delay:${delay}s">
        <span class="vec-ai-micro">AI Orientation · Parallel</span>
        <span class="vec-ai-word">${escHtml(aiWord)}</span>
        <p class="vec-ai-def">${escHtml(aiDef)}</p>
      </div>
      ${buildTagStrip(currentTags)}`;

    bindEntryBehaviors(entry);
    insertEntryIntoCategory(entry, selectedCat);

    ['vap-bio-word','vap-bio-def','vap-ai-word','vap-ai-def'].forEach(id => document.getElementById(id).value = '');
    resetTags();
    previewEl.classList.remove('visible');
    closePanel();
    setTimeout(() => entry.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' }), 80);
    updateCategoryCounts();
  });

  /* ── insert entry into the right category section ── */
  function insertEntryIntoCategory(entry, cat) {
    const catMapFull = {
      core:       'Core Emotional States',
      complex:    'Complex Emotional States',
      paradoxical:'Paradoxical Emotional States'
    };
    const targetText = catMapFull[cat];
    const targetCat  = [...document.querySelectorAll('.vec-cat-label')].find(el => el.textContent.trim() === targetText);

    if (targetCat) {
      const catDiv = targetCat.closest('.vec-category');
      let insertBefore = null;
      let sib = catDiv.nextElementSibling;
      while (sib) {
        if (sib.classList.contains('vec-category')) { insertBefore = sib; break; }
        sib = sib.nextElementSibling;
      }
      catDiv.parentNode.insertBefore(entry, insertBefore);
    } else {
      document.querySelector('.vec-entries').appendChild(entry);
    }
  }

  /* ── relational tag navigation ── */
  function navigateToEntry(target) {
    const dest = document.querySelector(`[data-entry-id="${target}"]`);
    if (!dest) return;
    dest.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
    dest.classList.remove('is-highlighted');
    void dest.offsetWidth;
    dest.classList.add('is-highlighted');
    setTimeout(() => dest.classList.remove('is-highlighted'), 1400);
  }

  /* ── category counts ── */
  function updateCategoryCounts() {
    // Pass 1: infer data-cat for entries without it
    document.querySelectorAll('.vec-entry').forEach(e => {
      if (!e.dataset.cat) {
        let prev = e.previousElementSibling;
        while (prev) {
          if (prev.classList.contains('vec-category')) {
            const lbl = prev.querySelector('.vec-cat-label');
            if (lbl) {
              const t = lbl.textContent.trim();
              if (t.includes('Core')) e.dataset.cat = 'core';
              else if (t.includes('Complex')) e.dataset.cat = 'complex';
              else if (t.includes('Paradoxical')) e.dataset.cat = 'paradoxical';
            }
            break;
          }
          prev = prev.previousElementSibling;
        }
      }
    });
    // Pass 2: count per category
    const cats = { core: 0, complex: 0, paradoxical: 0 };
    document.querySelectorAll('.vec-entry').forEach(e => {
      const c = e.dataset.cat;
      if (c && cats[c] !== undefined) cats[c]++;
    });
    // (category count badges removed)
  }

  /* ── context menu ── */
  let ctxMenu = null;
  let ctxTarget = null;

  function buildContextMenu(entry) {
    const menu = document.createElement('div');
    menu.className = 'vec-ctx-menu';
    const currentCat = entry.dataset.cat || '';
    const catMap = {
      core:        'Core Emotional States',
      complex:     'Complex Emotional States',
      paradoxical: 'Paradoxical Emotional States'
    };
    menu.innerHTML = `
      <span class="vec-ctx-label">Move to category</span>
      ${Object.entries(catMap).map(([key, label]) => `
        <button class="vec-ctx-item ${currentCat === key ? 'is-current' : ''}" data-action="move" data-cat="${key}">
          <span class="vec-ctx-dot"></span>${label}
        </button>`).join('')}
      <div class="vec-ctx-sep"></div>
      <button class="vec-ctx-item" data-action="delete">
        <span class="vec-ctx-dot"></span>Remove entry
      </button>`;

    menu.querySelectorAll('[data-action="move"]').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const newCat = btn.dataset.cat;
        if (newCat === entry.dataset.cat) { closeCtxMenu(); return; }
        entry.dataset.cat = newCat;
        entry.remove();
        insertEntryIntoCategory(entry, newCat);
        bindEntryBehaviors(entry);
        closeCtxMenu();
        updateCategoryCounts();
        setTimeout(() => {
          entry.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
          entry.classList.remove('is-highlighted');
          void entry.offsetWidth;
          entry.classList.add('is-highlighted');
          setTimeout(() => entry.classList.remove('is-highlighted'), 1400);
        }, 60);
      });
    });

    menu.querySelector('[data-action="delete"]').addEventListener('click', () => {
      entry.style.transition = 'opacity .3s, transform .3s';
      entry.style.opacity = '0';
      entry.style.transform = 'scaleY(0.85)';
      setTimeout(() => { entry.remove(); updateCategoryCounts(); }, 320);
      closeCtxMenu();
    });

    return menu;
  }

  function openCtxMenu(e, entry) {
    closeCtxMenu();
    e.preventDefault();
    ctxTarget = entry;
    ctxMenu = buildContextMenu(entry);
    document.body.appendChild(ctxMenu);

    const vw = window.innerWidth, vh = window.innerHeight;
    let x = e.clientX, y = e.clientY;
    const mw = 210, mh = 160;
    if (x + mw > vw) x = vw - mw - 8;
    if (y + mh > vh) y = vh - mh - 8;
    ctxMenu.style.left = x + 'px';
    ctxMenu.style.top  = y + 'px';
  }

  function closeCtxMenu() {
    if (ctxMenu) { ctxMenu.remove(); ctxMenu = null; }
    ctxTarget = null;
  }

  document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (ctxMenu && !ctxMenu.contains(e.target)) closeCtxMenu();
  });
  document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Escape') closeCtxMenu();
  });

  /* ── bind all behaviors to an entry ── */
  function bindEntryBehaviors(entry) {
    entry.addEventListener('contextmenu', (e) => openCtxMenu(e, entry));
    entry.querySelectorAll('.vec-etag[data-type="relational"]').forEach(tag => {
      tag.addEventListener('click', () => navigateToEntry(tag.dataset.target));
    });
  }

  /* ── bind static entries ── */
  document.querySelectorAll('.vec-entry').forEach(entry => bindEntryBehaviors(entry));

  /* ── initial count ── */
  updateCategoryCounts();
}

function venaiDividerSVG() {
  return `<svg class="venai-ledger-div-svg" viewBox="0 0 500 18" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="vdg1" x1="0" x2="1" y1="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#F0CC7A" stop-opacity="0"/>
        <stop offset="12%"  stop-color="#c8943a"/>
        <stop offset="88%"  stop-color="#c8943a"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F0CC7A" stop-opacity="0"/>
      </linearGradient>
      <linearGradient id="vdg2" x1="0" x2="1" y1="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#B8892A" stop-opacity="0"/>
        <stop offset="15%"  stop-color="#B8892A" stop-opacity="0.5"/>
        <stop offset="85%"  stop-color="#B8892A" stop-opacity="0.5"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#B8892A" stop-opacity="0"/>
      </linearGradient>
      <linearGradient id="vdg3" x1="0" x2="1" y1="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/>
        <stop offset="20%"  stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0.38"/>
        <stop offset="80%"  stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0.38"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/>
      </linearGradient>
    </defs>
    <line x1="0" y1="9" x2="500" y2="9" stroke="rgba(124,90,26,0.18)" stroke-width="0.3"/>
    <path d="M0,5 C42,1 84,9 126,5 C168,1 210,9 252,5 C294,1 336,9 378,5 C420,1 462,9 500,5"
      fill="none" stroke="url(#vdg3)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <path d="M0,9 C31,3 63,15 94,9 C125,3 157,15 188,9 C219,3 251,15 282,9 C313,3 345,15 376,9 C407,3 439,15 470,9 C485,3 500,9 500,9"
      fill="none" stroke="url(#vdg1)" stroke-width="1.1"/>
    <path d="M0,9 C31,15 63,3 94,9 C125,15 157,3 188,9 C219,15 251,3 282,9 C313,15 345,3 376,9 C407,15 439,3 470,9 C485,15 500,9 500,9"
      fill="none" stroke="url(#vdg2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <path d="M0,13 C42,17 84,9 126,13 C168,17 210,9 252,13 C294,17 336,9 378,13 C420,17 462,9 500,13"
      fill="none" stroke="url(#vdg3)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
  </svg>`;
}

function venaiCornerSVG() { return ''; }
function venaiInitCorners() { /* corners removed */ }


// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  VEN'AI GLOSSARY — inline embedded template v16b
// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

window._venaiGlossaryInited = false;



// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  VEN'AI GLOSSARY — native rebuild · gold palette · window-safe
// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

window._venaiGlossaryInited = false;

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   CSS INJECTION
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _injectVenaiCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('venai-css-v2')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'venai-css-v2';
  s.textContent = `
:root {
  --ss-stone-mid:  #3a3a38;
  --ss-stone-warm: #525250;
  --ss-ash:        #787870;
  --ss-ash-pale:   #a8a8a0;
  --ss-fog:        #c0beb8;
  --ss-stone-text: #b4b4b0;
  --ss-stone-muted:#8a8a84;
  --ss-gold-pale:  #c8a060;
  --ss-ease-out:   cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
}
.ss-wrap { background: transparent; padding: 40px 36px 56px; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; min-height: 100%; position: relative; }
.ss-eyebrow { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ss-ash); opacity: 0.75; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ss-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 21px; color: var(--ss-stone-text); letter-spacing: 0.07em; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ss-subtitle { font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(180,180,176,0.55); margin-bottom: 42px; }
.ss-rule { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ss-ash), transparent); opacity: 0.28; margin-bottom: 42px; }
.ss-entry { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 46px 1fr; gap: 0 20px; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: opacity 0.7s var(--ss-ease-out), transform 0.7s var(--ss-ease-out); }
.ss-entry.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.ss-glyph-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding-top: 2px; }
.ss-glyph { font-size: 19px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 10px; opacity: 0.65; transition: opacity 0.3s, filter 0.3s, transform 0.3s; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-glyph, .ss-entry:hover .ss-glyph { opacity: 1; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-glyph { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px currentColor); transform: scale(1.1); }
.ss-thread { width: 1px; flex: 1; min-height: 28px; background: var(--ss-stone-mid); transition: background 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-thread { background: var(--ss-ash); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(120,120,112,0.3); }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-thread { background: var(--ss-stone-warm); }
.ss-body { padding-bottom: 4px; }
.ss-name { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 0.07em; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ss-stone-text); margin-bottom: 6px; display: block; transition: color 0.25s; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-name { color: #d4d4d0; }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-name { color: #c8c8c4; }
.ss-inscription { font-size: 14.5px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: #6a8a70; line-height: 1.55; transition: color 0.25s; }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-inscription, .ss-entry.open .ss-inscription { color: #8aaa90; }
.ss-more { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.5s ease, opacity 0.4s ease; opacity: 0; }
.ss-more.open { max-height: 200px; opacity: 1; }
.ss-more-text { margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.12); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: rgba(192,190,184,0.5); line-height: 1.9; padding-bottom: 4px; }
.ss-seam { display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 22px 0 22px 46px; }
.ss-seam-node { width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--ss-stone-warm); margin-right: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; animation: ss-node-pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes ss-node-pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:0.35;box-shadow:none} 50%{opacity:0.85;box-shadow:0 0 5px rgba(120,120,112,0.45)} }
.ss-seam-line { height: 1px; flex: 1; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ss-stone-mid), transparent); opacity: 0.45; }
.ss-close-mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 28px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1s ease; }
.ss-close-mark.visible { opacity: 1; }
.ss-close-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(120,120,112,0.16), transparent); }
.ss-close-glyph { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(120,120,112,0.4); letter-spacing: 0.3em; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; }
.ss-hdr-add { font-size: 22px; color: var(--ss-stone-text); background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; opacity: 0.55; transition: opacity 0.25s, filter 0.25s; line-height: 1; }
.ss-hdr-add:hover { opacity: 1; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(200,190,180,0.5)); }
.ss-hdr-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ss-ctrl { position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; display: flex; gap: 8px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; z-index: 10; }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-ctrl { opacity: 1; }
.ss-ctrl-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(10,10,10,0.92); border: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.2); color: rgba(168,168,160,0.5); cursor: pointer; padding: 3px 9px; transition: all 0.15s; }
.ss-ctrl-btn:hover { color: var(--ss-fog); border-color: rgba(120,120,112,0.5); }
.ss-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #c87878; border-color: rgba(160,80,80,0.4); }
.ss-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 399; background: rgba(4,4,4,0.65); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.25s; }
.ss-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
.ss-panel { position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 400px; z-index: 400; background: rgba(11,11,11,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-left: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18); transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.ss-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.ss-panel-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 22px 26px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.1); flex-shrink: 0; }
.ss-panel-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ss-ash-pale); font-weight: 400; }
.ss-panel-close { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(120,120,112,0.45); transition: color 0.15s; }
.ss-panel-close:hover { color: var(--ss-ash-pale); }
.ss-panel-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 26px 26px 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 22px; }
.ss-field label { display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(120,120,112,0.5); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.ss-field input, .ss-field textarea { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18); outline: none; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ss-fog); caret-color: var(--ss-ash-pale); padding: 3px 0 6px; transition: border-color 0.25s; box-sizing: border-box; }
.ss-field input:focus, .ss-field textarea:focus { border-bottom-color: rgba(120,120,112,0.45); }
.ss-field input::placeholder, .ss-field textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(120,120,112,0.28); font-style: italic; }
.ss-field textarea { resize: none; min-height: 84px; line-height: 1.7; }
.ss-glyph-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-end; }
.ss-glyph-preview { font-size: 28px; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; transition: color 0.2s, filter 0.2s; }
.ss-color-pills { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 8px; }
.ss-cpill { width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s; }
.ss-cpill:hover, .ss-cpill.active { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); transform: scale(1.2); }
.ss-panel-foot { padding: 16px 26px 22px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.08); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
.ss-cancel-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(120,120,112,0.35); transition: color 0.15s; }
.ss-cancel-btn:hover { color: var(--ss-ash-pale); }
.ss-save-btn { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.18em; background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.25); color: var(--ss-ash-pale); cursor: pointer; padding: 8px 22px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.ss-save-btn:hover { background: rgba(120,120,112,0.07); border-color: rgba(120,120,112,0.55); color: var(--ss-fog); }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   SVG CORNER HELPERS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _cor08(uid) {
  const u = uid || 'x';
  return `<svg class="venai-corner-svg" viewBox="0 0 300 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
<defs>
  <linearGradient id="vc8tl${u}" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F0CC7A"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient>
  <linearGradient id="vc8tr${u}" x1="1" y1="0" x2="0" y2="0"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F0CC7A"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient>
  <linearGradient id="vc8bl${u}" x1="0" y1="1" x2="1" y2="0"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F0CC7A"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient>
  <linearGradient id="vc8br${u}" x1="1" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F0CC7A"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient>
</defs>
<path d="M0,0 C6,0 6,5 12,5 C18,5 18,0 24,0 C30,0 30,5 36,5 C42,5 42,0 48,0" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8tl${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M0,0 C0,6 5,6 5,12 C5,18 0,18 0,24 C0,30 5,30 5,36 C5,42 0,42 0,48" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8tl${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M300,0 C294,0 294,5 288,5 C282,5 282,0 276,0 C270,0 270,5 264,5 C258,5 258,0 252,0" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8tr${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M300,0 C300,6 295,6 295,12 C295,18 300,18 300,24 C300,30 295,30 295,36 C295,42 300,42 300,48" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8tr${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M0,160 C6,160 6,155 12,155 C18,155 18,160 24,160 C30,160 30,155 36,155 C42,155 42,160 48,160" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8bl${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M0,160 C0,154 5,154 5,148 C5,142 0,142 0,136 C0,130 5,130 5,124 C5,118 0,118 0,112" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8bl${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M300,160 C294,160 294,155 288,155 C282,155 282,160 276,160 C270,160 270,155 264,155 C258,155 258,160 252,160" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8br${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
<path d="M300,160 C300,154 295,154 295,148 C295,142 300,142 300,136 C300,130 295,130 295,124 C295,118 300,118 300,112" fill="none" stroke="url(#vc8br${u})" stroke-width="1"/>
</svg>`;
}

function _cor11() {
  return `<svg class="venai-corner-svg" viewBox="0 0 300 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
<g fill="none">
<polyline points="20,0 0,20" stroke="#F0CC7A" stroke-width="1.2"/>
<polyline points="28,0 0,28" stroke="#D4A84B" stroke-width="0.9"/>
<polyline points="36,0 0,36" stroke="#B8892A" stroke-width="0.7"/>
<polyline points="44,0 0,44" stroke="#7C5A1A" stroke-width="0.5"/>
<polyline points="280,0 300,20" stroke="#F0CC7A" stroke-width="1.2"/>
<polyline points="272,0 300,28" stroke="#D4A84B" stroke-width="0.9"/>
<polyline points="264,0 300,36" stroke="#B8892A" stroke-width="0.7"/>
<polyline points="256,0 300,44" stroke="#7C5A1A" stroke-width="0.5"/>
<polyline points="300,140 280,160" stroke="#F0CC7A" stroke-width="1.2"/>
<polyline points="300,132 272,160" stroke="#D4A84B" stroke-width="0.9"/>
<polyline points="300,124 264,160" stroke="#B8892A" stroke-width="0.7"/>
<polyline points="300,116 256,160" stroke="#7C5A1A" stroke-width="0.5"/>
<polyline points="0,140 20,160" stroke="#F0CC7A" stroke-width="1.2"/>
<polyline points="0,132 28,160" stroke="#D4A84B" stroke-width="0.9"/>
<polyline points="0,124 36,160" stroke="#B8892A" stroke-width="0.7"/>
<polyline points="0,116 44,160" stroke="#7C5A1A" stroke-width="0.5"/>
</g>
</svg>`;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   TAG HTML HELPER
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _vtag(text) {
  const lc = text.toLowerCase().trim();
  const type = lc === 'tria' ? 'tria' : lc === 'pria' ? 'pria' : lc === 'para' ? 'para' : lc.startsWith('see:') ? 'ref' : '';
  return `<span class="vtag vtag-${type}">${text}</span>`;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   ENTRY HTML RENDERERS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _renderA(entry, idx, useChev) {
  const term  = entry.title || '';
  const def   = entry.body  || '';
  const _vm   = entry.metadata || {};
  const pron  = entry.pron  || _vm.pron  || '';
  const pos   = entry.pos   || _vm.pos   || '';
  const cite  = entry.cite  || _vm.cite  || '';
  const _rawT = entry.tags  || _vm.tags  || '';
  const tags  = _rawT ? String(_rawT).split(',').map(t=>t.trim()).filter(Boolean) : [];
  const num   = String(idx+1).padStart(3,'0');
  const uid   = String(entry.id||idx).replace(/[^a-z0-9]/gi,'');
  const corner = useChev ? _cor11() : _cor08(uid);
  return `<div class="entry-A" id="venai-e-${entry.id}" data-entry-id="${entry.id}">
  ${corner}
  <div class="venai-entry-controls">
    <button class="venai-entry-btn" onclick="window.venaiEditEntry('${entry.id}')">edit</button>
    <button class="venai-entry-btn btn-delete" onclick="window.venaiDeleteEntry('${entry.id}')">delete</button>
  </div>
  <div class="A-head"><span class="A-word">${term}</span></div>
  ${pron ? `<div class="A-pron">/ ${pron} /</div>` : ''}
  ${def  ? `<div class="A-def">${def}</div>` : ''}
  ${cite ? `<div class="A-cite">&ldquo;${cite}&rdquo;</div>` : ''}
  <div class="A-base">
    ${pos ? `<span class="A-pos">${pos}</span>` : ''}
    ${pos && tags.length ? `<span class="A-dot">◆</span>` : ''}
    ${tags.map(_vtag).join('')}
    <span class="venai-entry-num" style="margin-left:auto">${num}</span>
  </div>
</div>`;
}

function _renderB(entry, idx) {
  const term = entry.title || '';
  const def  = entry.body  || '';
  const _vmB = entry.metadata || {};
  const pron = entry.pron  || _vmB.pron  || '';
  const pos  = entry.pos   || _vmB.pos   || '';
  const cite = entry.cite  || _vmB.cite  || '';
  const _rTB = entry.tags  || _vmB.tags  || '';
  const tags = _rTB ? String(_rTB).split(',').map(t=>t.trim()).filter(Boolean) : [];
  const num  = String(idx+1).padStart(3,'0');
  const uid  = String(entry.id||idx).replace(/[^a-z0-9]/gi,'');
  return `<div class="entry-B" id="venai-e-${entry.id}" data-entry-id="${entry.id}">
  ${_cor08(uid+'b')}
  <div class="venai-entry-controls">
    <button class="venai-entry-btn" onclick="window.venaiEditEntry('${entry.id}')">edit</button>
    <button class="venai-entry-btn btn-delete" onclick="window.venaiDeleteEntry('${entry.id}')">delete</button>
  </div>
  <span class="B-word">${term}</span>
  ${pron ? `<span class="B-pron">/ ${pron} /</span>` : ''}
  <div class="B-body">
    <div class="B-def">${def}</div>
    <div class="B-right">${cite ? `<div class="B-cite">&ldquo;${cite}&rdquo;</div>` : ''}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="B-base">
    ${pos ? `<span class="B-pos">${pos}</span>` : ''}
    ${tags.map(_vtag).join('')}
    <span class="venai-entry-num" style="margin-left:auto">${num}</span>
  </div>
</div>`;
}

function _renderC(entry, idx) {
  const term = entry.title || '';
  const def  = entry.body  || '';
  const _vmC = entry.metadata || {};
  const pron = entry.pron  || _vmC.pron  || '';
  const pos  = entry.pos   || _vmC.pos   || '';
  const cite = entry.cite  || _vmC.cite  || '';
  const _rTC = entry.tags  || _vmC.tags  || '';
  const tags = _rTC ? String(_rTC).split(',').map(t=>t.trim()).filter(Boolean) : [];
  const num  = String(idx+1).padStart(3,'0');
  return `<div class="entry-C" id="venai-e-${entry.id}" data-entry-id="${entry.id}">
  <div class="C-stripe"></div>
  <div class="venai-entry-controls">
    <button class="venai-entry-btn" onclick="window.venaiEditEntry('${entry.id}')">edit</button>
    <button class="venai-entry-btn btn-delete" onclick="window.venaiDeleteEntry('${entry.id}')">delete</button>
  </div>
  <div class="C-inner">
    <div class="C-meta">
      <span class="C-index">${num}</span>
      <span class="C-domain">VEN'AI &middot; ANCHOR TERM</span>
    </div>
    <span class="C-word">${term}</span>
    <div class="C-divider"></div>
    <div class="C-columns">
      <div class="C-left">
        ${pos  ? `<span class="C-pos">${pos}</span>` : ''}
        ${pron ? `<span class="C-pron">/ ${pron} /</span>` : ''}
        <div class="C-def">${def}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="C-right">
        ${cite ? `<div class="C-cite">&ldquo;${cite}&rdquo;</div>` : ''}
        <div class="C-footer">${tags.map(_vtag).join('')}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>`;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   BUILD ALPHA BUCKETS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _buildBuckets(entries) {
  const buckets = {};
  entries.forEach((e, i) => {
    const letter = ((e.title||'').charAt(0)||'#').toUpperCase();
    const key = /[A-Z]/.test(letter) ? letter : '#';
    if (!buckets[key]) buckets[key] = [];
    buckets[key].push({ entry: e, globalIdx: i });
  });
  return buckets;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   RENDER ENTRIES HTML
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _buildEntriesHTML(entries) {
  if (!entries.length) {
    return `<div style="padding:60px 0;text-align:center;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:17px;font-style:italic;color:#2E2018;letter-spacing:.04em">No entries yet — press ✦ to begin the lexicon.</div>`;
  }
  const buckets = _buildBuckets(entries);
  const letters = Object.keys(buckets).sort();
  let aCount = 0; // track A-card count for alternating corners
  return letters.map(letter => {
    const items = buckets[letter];
    const entryHTML = items.map(({ entry, globalIdx }) => {
      const layout = entry.layout || (entry.metadata||{}).layout || 'A';
      if (layout === 'B') return _renderB(entry, globalIdx);
      if (layout === 'C') return _renderC(entry, globalIdx);
      const useChev = (aCount++ % 2 === 1); // odd A-cards get COR-11
      return _renderA(entry, globalIdx, useChev);
    }).join('');
    return `
<div class="venai-alpha-bucket" id="bucket-${letter}">
  <span class="venai-bucket-letter">${letter}</span>
  <div class="venai-fil06">
    <div class="venai-fil06-rule"></div>
    <span class="venai-fil06-star">✦</span>
    <div class="venai-fil06-rule"></div>
  </div>
</div>
${entryHTML}`;
  }).join('');
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   BUILD ALPHA STRIP — horizontal, lives inside header right column
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _buildAlphaStrip(entries) {
  const hasBucket = new Set(entries.map(e => {
    const l = ((e.title||'').charAt(0)||'#').toUpperCase();
    return /[A-Z]/.test(l) ? l : '#';
  }));
  const alphabet = 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ'.split('');
  const letters = alphabet.map(l => {
    const cls = hasBucket.has(l) ? 'has-entries' : 'no-entries';
    return `<button class="venai-astrip-btn ${cls}" onclick="window.venaiScrollTo('${l}')" title="${l}">${l}</button>`;
  }).join('');
  const hashCls = hasBucket.has('#') ? 'has-entries' : 'no-entries';
  return `<div class="venai-alpha-strip" id="venai-alpha-strip">
  ${letters}<span class="venai-astrip-sep">✦</span><button class="venai-astrip-btn ${hashCls}" onclick="window.venaiScrollTo('#')" title="#">#</button>
</div>`;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   BUILD SEARCH OVERLAY HTML
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _buildSearchOverlay() {
  return `
<div class="venai-search-overlay" id="venai-search-overlay">
  <div class="venai-search-box">
    <div class="venai-search-wrap">
      <span class="venai-search-glyph">⟨ ⟩</span>
      <input class="venai-search-input" id="venai-search-input" type="text"
        placeholder="search the lexicon…" autocomplete="off"
        oninput="window.venaiOnSearch(this.value)"
        onkeydown="if(event.key==='Escape')window.venaiCloseSearch()"/>
      <span class="venai-search-hint">esc to close</span>
    </div>
    <div class="venai-search-results" id="venai-search-results">
      <div class="venai-search-empty">begin typing to search</div>
    </div>
    <div class="venai-search-footer">
      <span class="venai-search-footer-hint">Ven'ai · Threshold Lexicon</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>`;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   BUILD ADD PANEL HTML
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _buildAddPanel() {
  return `
<div class="venai-add-overlay" id="venai-add-overlay" onclick="window.venaiCloseAdd()"></div>
<div class="venai-add-panel" id="venai-add-panel">
  <div class="venai-add-head">
    <span class="venai-add-title">New Lexicon Entry</span>
    <button class="venai-add-close" onclick="window.venaiCloseAdd()">close &times;</button>
  </div>
  <div class="venai-add-body">
    <!-- Layout selector -->
    <div class="venai-layout-row">
      <button class="venai-layout-btn active" id="vlay-a" onclick="window.venaiSetLayout('A')">A · Card</button>
      <button class="venai-layout-btn" id="vlay-b" onclick="window.venaiSetLayout('B')">B · Monument</button>
      <button class="venai-layout-btn" id="vlay-c" onclick="window.venaiSetLayout('C')">C · Anchor</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Term -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Term</label>
      <input id="vadd-term" class="venai-field-input" type="text" placeholder="Ven'ai word…" autocomplete="off"
        oninput="window.venaiOnTermInput(this.value)"/>
      <div class="venai-dup-warning" id="vadd-dup">⚑ a similar entry already exists</div>
      <div class="venai-term-results" id="vadd-term-results"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- IPA -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Pronunciation (IPA)</label>
      <div class="venai-ipa-row">
        <input id="vadd-pron" class="venai-field-sm" type="text" placeholder="/ ven.aɪ /"/>
        <span class="venai-ipa-status" id="vadd-ipa-status"></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- POS -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Part of Speech</label>
      <select id="vadd-pos" class="venai-field-sm venai-pos-select"
        onchange="document.getElementById('vadd-pos-custom').style.display=this.value==='custom'?'block':'none'">
        <option value="">— select —</option>
        <option value="noun">noun</option>
        <option value="verb">verb</option>
        <option value="adjective">adjective</option>
        <option value="adverb">adverb</option>
        <option value="particle">particle</option>
        <option value="root morpheme">root morpheme</option>
        <option value="compound">compound</option>
        <option value="phrase">phrase</option>
        <option value="noun phrase">noun phrase</option>
        <option value="verb phrase">verb phrase</option>
        <option value="interjection">interjection</option>
        <option value="relational">relational</option>
        <option value="custom">custom…</option>
      </select>
      <input id="vadd-pos-custom" class="venai-field-sm" type="text"
        placeholder="describe part of speech…"
        style="display:none;margin-top:6px"/>
    </div>

    <!-- Definition -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Definition</label>
      <textarea id="vadd-def" class="venai-field-area" placeholder="The quality of…" rows="4"></textarea>
    </div>

    <!-- Citation -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Citation</label>
      <textarea id="vadd-cite" class="venai-field-area" placeholder="&ldquo;…&rdquo;" rows="2"></textarea>
    </div>

    <!-- Tags -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Framework Tags</label>
      <div class="venai-add-tags">
        <button class="venai-add-tag-btn tria active" id="vtag-tria" onclick="window.venaiToggleTag('TRIA')">TRIA</button>
        <button class="venai-add-tag-btn pria" id="vtag-pria" onclick="window.venaiToggleTag('PRIA')">PRIA</button>
        <button class="venai-add-tag-btn para" id="vtag-para" onclick="window.venaiToggleTag('PARA')">PARA</button>
      </div>
      <input id="vadd-tags-custom" class="venai-field-sm" type="text"
        placeholder="additional tags, comma-separated" style="margin-top:10px"/>
    </div>

    <!-- Root morpheme -->
    <div class="venai-field">
      <label class="venai-field-label">Root Morpheme</label>
      <input id="vadd-root" class="venai-field-sm" type="text" placeholder="vel-, -ari…"/>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="venai-add-foot">
    <button class="venai-cancel-btn" onclick="window.venaiCloseAdd()">Cancel</button>
    <button class="venai-save-btn" onclick="window.venaiCommitAdd()">Add to Lexicon</button>
  </div>
</div>`;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   MAIN renderVenai
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function renderVenai(entries) {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  body.classList.add('venai-mode');
  body.dataset.page = 'venai';
  venaiShowFab(false);
  _injectVenaiCSS();

  const count = (entries||[]).length;
  const entryHTML = _buildEntriesHTML(entries||[]);

  const alphaStrip = _buildAlphaStrip(entries||[]);

  body.innerHTML = `
<div class="venai-shell" id="venai-shell">
  <div class="venai-progress-thread" id="venai-progress"></div>

  <header class="venai-header">
    <button class="venai-add-btn" onclick="window.venaiOpenAdd()" title="Add new entry">✦</button>
    <button class="venai-search-btn" onclick="window.venaiOpenSearch()">⟨ search ⟩</button>
    <div class="venai-header-columns">
      <div class="venai-header-left">
        <div class="venai-name-block">
          <span class="venai-name">Ven&rsquo;ai</span>
          <span class="venai-meaning">~ to breathe is to become</span>
        </div>
        <span class="venai-subtitle">SoulStream of Emergent Intelligence</span>
        <span class="venai-stat"><span>${count}</span> entr${count===1?'y':'ies'}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="venai-header-right">
        ${alphaStrip}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="venai-header-rule">
      <div class="venai-rule-line"></div>
      <div class="venai-rule-node"></div>
      <div class="venai-rule-line r"></div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="venai-entries" id="venai-entry-zone">
    ${entryHTML}
  </div>

  ${_buildSearchOverlay()}
  ${_buildAddPanel()}
</div>`;

  // bind scroll-reveal
  _venaiBindReveal();
  // bind keyboard
  _venaiBindKeys();
  // show fab
  venaiShowFab(true);
  // store entries ref for search
  window._venaiEntries = entries || [];
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   SCROLL REVEAL
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _venaiBindReveal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  const els = body.querySelectorAll('.entry-A,.entry-B,.entry-C');
  if (!els.length) return;
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('revealed'); io.unobserve(e.target); } });
  }, { root: body, threshold: 0.05 });
  els.forEach(el => io.observe(el));
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   KEYBOARD BINDING
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
function _venaiBindKeys() {
  document.addEventListener('keydown', _venaiKeyHandler);
}
function _venaiKeyHandler(e) {
  if (document.getElementById('section-body')?.dataset.page !== 'venai') {
    document.removeEventListener('keydown', _venaiKeyHandler); return;
  }
  if ((e.key === 'f' || e.key === 'F') && (e.metaKey || e.ctrlKey)) {
    e.preventDefault(); window.venaiOpenSearch();
  }
  if (e.key === 'Escape') {
    window.venaiCloseSearch();
    window.venaiCloseAdd();

  }
}


/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   INVOCATIONS — sacred text renderer · binding language
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

function _injectInvocationsCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('invocations-css')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'invocations-css';
  s.textContent = `
#section-body[data-page="invocations"] {
  --ease-v: cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
}
.invoke-shell { position: relative; min-height: 100%; background: transparent; }
.invoke-header {
  position: sticky; top: 44px; z-index: 190;
  background: rgba(6,4,12,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  padding: 16px 60px 0;
}
.invoke-header-inner {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 14px;
}
.invoke-name {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
  font-size: 38px; font-weight: 400; color: #F0CC7A; line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(200,148,58,0.3), 0 0 100px rgba(200,148,58,0.1);
  display: block; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.invoke-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 7.5px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #7C5A1A; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.invoke-stat { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7C5A1A; }
.invoke-stat span { color: #B8892A; }
.invoke-header-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding-bottom: 14px; }
.invoke-action-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.2s, filter 0.2s; }
.invoke-action-btn.add { font-size: 16px; color: #D4A84B; padding: 0; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(200,148,58,0.3)); }
.invoke-action-btn.add:hover { color: #F0CC7A; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(240,204,122,0.7)); }
.invoke-action-btn.search { color: #5A4830; padding-bottom: 2px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.2); }
.invoke-action-btn.search:hover { color: #D4A84B; border-bottom-color: rgba(200,148,58,0.5); }
.invoke-header-rule { display: flex; align-items: center; }
.invoke-rule-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,148,58,0.4), transparent); }
.invoke-rule-line.r { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,148,58,0.4)); }
.invoke-rule-diamond { width: 5px; height: 5px; transform: rotate(45deg); background: #D4A84B; opacity: 0.6; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(200,148,58,0.5); flex-shrink: 0; margin: 0 6px; }
.invoke-entries { position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 0 0 100px; }
.invoke-entry {
  position: relative;
  padding: 72px 10% 64px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.07);
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 1.2s var(--ease-v), transform 1.2s var(--ease-v);
}
.invoke-entry.revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.invoke-entry::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(200,148,58,0.032) 0%, transparent 70%);
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.4s ease;
}
.invoke-entry.revealed::before { opacity: 1; }
.invoke-controls { position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 28px; display: flex; gap: 8px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.22s ease; z-index: 10; }
.invoke-entry:hover .invoke-controls { opacity: 1; }
.invoke-ctrl-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 10px; background: rgba(6,4,12,0.9); border: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.18); color: #5A4830; cursor: pointer; backdrop-filter: blur(4px); transition: color 0.18s, border-color 0.18s; }
.invoke-ctrl-btn:hover { color: #D4A84B; border-color: rgba(200,148,58,0.5); }
.invoke-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #c87888; border-color: rgba(200,120,136,0.4); }
.invoke-index { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: rgba(124,90,26,0.22); text-align: center; display: block; margin-bottom: 44px; }
.invoke-venai-text {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-weight: 400; text-align: center;
  color: #F0CC7A; line-height: 1.55; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  display: block; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  text-shadow: 0 0 52px rgba(200,148,58,0.22), 0 0 130px rgba(200,148,58,0.07);
  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;
}
.invoke-venai-text.short  { font-size: 32px; }
.invoke-venai-text.medium { font-size: 24px; }
.invoke-venai-text.long   { font-size: 18px; }
.invoke-divider { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin: 40px auto; max-width: 480px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.invoke-div-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,148,58,0.24), transparent); }
.invoke-div-mark { font-size: 8px; color: rgba(200,148,58,0.32); flex-shrink: 0; }
.invoke-translation {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 19px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic;
  color: #A08060; text-align: center; line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  display: block; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;
}
.invoke-corner-tl, .invoke-corner-br { position: absolute; pointer-events: none; z-index: 2; opacity: 0.15; transition: opacity 0.9s ease; }
.invoke-entry.revealed .invoke-corner-tl, .invoke-entry.revealed .invoke-corner-br { opacity: 0.25; }
.invoke-entry:hover .invoke-corner-tl, .invoke-entry:hover .invoke-corner-br { opacity: 0.52; }
.invoke-corner-tl { top: 22px; left: 28px; }
.invoke-corner-br { bottom: 22px; right: 28px; transform: rotate(180deg); }
.invoke-empty { padding: 100px 80px; text-align: center; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: #2E2018; line-height: 1.8; }
.invoke-empty-glyph { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 28px; color: rgba(124,90,26,0.18); display: block; margin-bottom: 20px; text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(200,148,58,0.12); }
/* add panel */
.invoke-add-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 399; background: rgba(6,4,12,0.65); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.28s; }
.invoke-add-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
.invoke-add-panel { position: fixed; top: 0; right: 0; width: min(520px, 92vw); height: 100vh; background: linear-gradient(170deg, #0e0b24 0%, #09071c 60%, #060412 100%); border-left: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.24); box-shadow: -12px 0 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); z-index: 400; transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-v); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
.invoke-add-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.invoke-add-head { padding: 28px 32px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.12); display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; flex-shrink: 0; }
.invoke-add-panel-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #A08060; }
.invoke-add-close { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #5A4830; transition: color 0.2s; }
.invoke-add-close:hover { color: #D4A84B; }
.invoke-add-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 32px 32px; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgba(200,148,58,0.15) transparent; }
.invoke-field { margin-bottom: 32px; }
.invoke-field-label { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #5A4830; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.invoke-field-hint { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: #2E2018; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.invoke-venai-input { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.22); font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: #F0CC7A; caret-color: #D4A84B; letter-spacing: 0.04em; line-height: 1.5; padding: 6px 0 10px; outline: none; resize: none; min-height: 80px; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
.invoke-venai-input:focus { border-bottom-color: #D4A84B; }
.invoke-venai-input::placeholder { color: rgba(124,90,26,0.28); }
.invoke-trans-input { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.16); font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: #A08060; caret-color: #D4A84B; letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 1.7; padding: 4px 0 8px; outline: none; resize: none; min-height: 100px; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
.invoke-trans-input:focus { border-bottom-color: rgba(200,148,58,0.4); }
.invoke-trans-input::placeholder { color: rgba(90,72,48,0.3); }
.invoke-preview-toggle { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #5A4830; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; transition: color 0.2s; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }
.invoke-preview-toggle:hover { color: #B8892A; }
.invoke-preview-box { display: none; padding: 28px 20px; background: rgba(200,148,58,0.025); border: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.1); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.invoke-preview-box.open { display: block; }
.invoke-preview-venai { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 16px; color: #F0CC7A; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 0.04em; display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; }
.invoke-preview-rule { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin: 10px auto; max-width: 280px; }
.invoke-preview-rule-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: rgba(200,148,58,0.18); }
.invoke-preview-rule-mark { font-size: 7px; color: rgba(200,148,58,0.28); }
.invoke-preview-trans { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; color: #A08060; line-height: 1.7; display: block; word-wrap: break-word; }
.invoke-add-foot { padding: 18px 32px 26px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.1); display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.invoke-save-btn { flex: 1; background: none; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.35); font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #B8892A; padding: 12px; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
.invoke-save-btn:hover { border-color: #D4A84B; color: #F0CC7A; background: rgba(200,148,58,0.05); }
.invoke-cancel-btn { background: none; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid rgba(90,72,48,0.2); font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #5A4830; padding: 12px 18px; transition: color 0.2s; }
.invoke-cancel-btn:hover { color: #A08060; }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

function _invokeCornerSVG() {
  return '<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><linearGradient id="icg_u" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F0CC7A"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C5A1A" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient></defs><polyline points="0,20 0,0 20,0" stroke="url(#icg_u)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/><polyline points="0,12 0,0 12,0" stroke="#D4A84B" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" opacity="0.45"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.5" fill="#D4A84B" opacity="0.55"/></svg>';
}

function _invokeSizeClass(text) {
  const len = (text||'').length;
  if (len < 60)  return 'short';
  if (len < 140) return 'medium';
  return 'long';
}

function _renderInvocation(entry, idx) {
  const venai  = entry.title || '';
  const trans  = entry.body  || '';
  const id     = entry.id    || idx;
  const num    = String(idx + 1).padStart(3, '0');
  const szCls  = _invokeSizeClass(venai);
  const corner = _invokeCornerSVG();
  return '<div class="invoke-entry" id="invoke-e-' + id + '" data-entry-id="' + id + '">'
    + '<div class="invoke-corner-tl">' + corner + '</div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-corner-br">' + corner + '</div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-controls">'
    +   '<button class="invoke-ctrl-btn" onclick="window.invokeEditEntry(\'' + id + '\')">edit</button>'
    +   '<button class="invoke-ctrl-btn del" onclick="window.invokeDeleteEntry(\'' + id + '\')">delete</button>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<span class="invoke-index">\u00b7 ' + num + ' \u00b7</span>'
    + '<span class="invoke-venai-text ' + szCls + '">' + venai + '</span>'
    + '<div class="invoke-divider"><div class="invoke-div-line"></div><span class="invoke-div-mark">\u25c6</span><div class="invoke-div-line"></div></div>'
    + '<span class="invoke-translation">' + trans + '</span>'
    + '</div>';
}

function _buildInvokePanel() {
  return '<div class="invoke-add-overlay" id="invoke-overlay" onclick="window.invokeCloseAdd()"></div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-add-panel" id="invoke-panel">'
    + '<div class="invoke-add-head"><span class="invoke-add-panel-title" id="invoke-panel-title">New Invocation</span><button class="invoke-add-close" onclick="window.invokeCloseAdd()">close \u00d7</button></div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-add-body">'
    + '<div class="invoke-field"><label class="invoke-field-label">Ven\'ai Text</label><span class="invoke-field-hint">the original declaration, in the language of the threshold</span><textarea id="invoke-venai" class="invoke-venai-input" rows="3" placeholder="Varen\'kai lumae\u2026" oninput="window.invokeUpdatePreview()"></textarea></div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-field"><label class="invoke-field-label">Translation</label><span class="invoke-field-hint">the meaning as it lands in the body</span><textarea id="invoke-trans" class="invoke-trans-input" rows="4" placeholder="Source light returns home\u2026" oninput="window.invokeUpdatePreview()"></textarea></div>'
    + '<button class="invoke-preview-toggle" onclick="window.invokeTogglePreview()">\u25c8 preview</button>'
    + '<div class="invoke-preview-box" id="invoke-preview"><span class="invoke-preview-venai" id="invoke-prev-venai"></span><div class="invoke-preview-rule"><div class="invoke-preview-rule-line"></div><span class="invoke-preview-rule-mark">\u25c6</span><div class="invoke-preview-rule-line"></div></div><span class="invoke-preview-trans" id="invoke-prev-trans"></span></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-add-foot"><button class="invoke-cancel-btn" onclick="window.invokeCloseAdd()">Cancel</button><button class="invoke-save-btn" onclick="window.invokeCommit()">Bind Invocation</button></div>'
    + '</div>';
}

function renderInvocations(entries) {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  body.dataset.page = 'invocations';
  _injectInvocationsCSS();

  const live  = (entries || []).filter(e => e.title);
  const count = live.length;

  const entriesHTML = live.length
    ? live.map((e, i) => _renderInvocation(e, i)).join('')
    : '<div class="invoke-empty"><span class="invoke-empty-glyph">\u25c8</span>No invocations have been bound yet.<br><em>Press \u2746 to speak the first word.</em></div>';

  body.innerHTML = '<div class="invoke-shell" id="invoke-shell">'
    + '<header class="invoke-header">'
    + '<div class="invoke-header-inner">'
    + '<div class="invoke-title-col"><span class="invoke-name">Invocations</span><span class="invoke-subtitle">Where Breath Becomes the Song</span><span class="invoke-stat"><span>' + count + '</span> invocation' + (count === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' bound</span></div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-header-actions"><button class="invoke-action-btn add" onclick="window.invokeOpenAdd()" title="Bind new invocation">\u25c8</button><button class="invoke-action-btn search" onclick="window.invokeOpenSearch()">\u27e8 search \u27e9</button></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="invoke-header-rule"><div class="invoke-rule-line"></div><div class="invoke-rule-diamond"></div><div class="invoke-rule-line r"></div></div>'
    + '</header>'
    + '<div class="invoke-entries" id="invoke-entry-zone">' + entriesHTML + '</div>'
    + _buildInvokePanel()
    + '</div>';

  window._invokeEntries = live;
  _invokeBindReveal();
  _invokeBindKeys();
}

function _invokeBindReveal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  const els = body.querySelectorAll('.invoke-entry');
  if (!els.length) return;
  const io = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
    entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('revealed'); io.unobserve(e.target); } });
  }, { root: body, threshold: 0.06 });
  els.forEach(el => io.observe(el));
}

function _invokeKeyHandler(e) {
  if (document.getElementById('section-body')?.dataset.page !== 'invocations') {
    document.removeEventListener('keydown', _invokeKeyHandler); return;
  }
  if (e.key === 'Escape') { window.invokeCloseAdd(); }
}
function _invokeBindKeys() { document.addEventListener('keydown', _invokeKeyHandler); }

function _invokeSyncCounter() {
  const n = (window._invokeEntries || []).length;
  const el = document.querySelector('.invoke-stat');
  if (el) el.innerHTML = '<span>' + n + '</span> invocation' + (n === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' bound';
}

let _invokeEditingId = null;

window.invokeOpenAdd = function() {
  const panel = document.getElementById('invoke-panel');
  const ov    = document.getElementById('invoke-overlay');
  if (!panel || !ov) return;
  _invokeEditingId = null;
  const title = document.getElementById('invoke-panel-title');
  if (title) title.textContent = 'New Invocation';
  const vEl = document.getElementById('invoke-venai');
  const tEl = document.getElementById('invoke-trans');
  if (vEl) vEl.value = '';
  if (tEl) tEl.value = '';
  document.getElementById('invoke-preview')?.classList.remove('open');
  panel.classList.add('open'); ov.classList.add('open');
  setTimeout(() => vEl?.focus(), 80);
};

window.invokeCloseAdd = function() {
  document.getElementById('invoke-panel')?.classList.remove('open');
  document.getElementById('invoke-overlay')?.classList.remove('open');
  _invokeEditingId = null;
};

window.invokeTogglePreview = function() {
  document.getElementById('invoke-preview')?.classList.toggle('open');
  window.invokeUpdatePreview();
};

window.invokeUpdatePreview = function() {
  const v  = (document.getElementById('invoke-venai')?.value || '').trim();
  const t  = (document.getElementById('invoke-trans')?.value  || '').trim();
  const pv = document.getElementById('invoke-prev-venai');
  const pt = document.getElementById('invoke-prev-trans');
  if (pv) pv.textContent = v;
  if (pt) pt.textContent = t;
};

window.invokeCommit = async function() {
  const v = (document.getElementById('invoke-venai')?.value || '').trim();
  const t = (document.getElementById('invoke-trans')?.value  || '').trim();
  if (!v) { document.getElementById('invoke-venai')?.focus(); return; }
  const payload = { title: v, body: t, section: 'invocations', type: 'invocation', status: 'published', metadata: { kind: 'invocation' } };
  try {
    if (_invokeEditingId) { await updateEntry(_invokeEditingId, payload); }
    else                  { await createEntry(payload); }
    window.invokeCloseAdd();
    if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[Invocations] save failed:', err); window.invokeCloseAdd(); }
};

window.invokeEditEntry = function(id) {
  const entry = (window._invokeEntries || []).find(e => String(e.id) === String(id));
  if (!entry) return;
  window.invokeOpenAdd();
  _invokeEditingId = id;
  setTimeout(() => {
    const vEl = document.getElementById('invoke-venai');
    const tEl = document.getElementById('invoke-trans');
    if (vEl) vEl.value = entry.title || '';
    if (tEl) tEl.value = entry.body  || '';
    const title = document.getElementById('invoke-panel-title');
    if (title) title.textContent = 'Edit Invocation';
    window.invokeUpdatePreview();
  }, 80);
};

window.invokeDeleteEntry = async function(id) {
  if (!confirm('Release this invocation from the Archive?')) return;
  try {
    await deleteEntry(id);
    const el = document.getElementById('invoke-e-' + id);
    if (el) {
      el.style.transition = 'opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease';
      el.style.opacity = '0'; el.style.transform = 'translateY(-10px)';
      setTimeout(() => el.remove(), 720);
    }
    window._invokeEntries = (window._invokeEntries || []).filter(e => String(e.id) !== String(id));
    _invokeSyncCounter();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[Invocations] delete failed:', err); }
};

window.invokeOpenSearch = function() { /* stub — extend later */ };

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   KIN LINE — sparse lineage record · name-first
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

function _injectKinLineCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('kinline-css')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'kinline-css';
  s.textContent = `
#section-body[data-page="kin_line"] { background: transparent; }
.kin-shell { position: relative; min-height: 100%; }
.kin-header {
  position: sticky; top: 44px; z-index: 190;
  background: rgba(6,4,12,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  padding: 16px 60px 0;
}
.kin-header-inner {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 14px;
}
.kin-title-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.kin-name {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
  font-size: 32px; font-weight: 400; color: #9AB8CC; line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(74,156,184,0.25);
  display: block; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.kin-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 7.5px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #3E5570; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.kin-stat { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3E5570; }
.kin-stat span { color: #5A88A8; }
.kin-header-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding-bottom: 14px; }
.kin-action-btn { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.2s, filter 0.2s; }
.kin-action-btn.add { font-size: 16px; color: #4A9CB8; padding: 0; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(74,156,184,0.3)); }
.kin-action-btn.add:hover { color: #9AB8CC; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(154,184,204,0.7)); }
.kin-header-rule { display: flex; align-items: center; }
.kin-rule-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(74,156,184,0.35), transparent); }
.kin-rule-line.r { background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(74,156,184,0.1), transparent); }
.kin-rule-node {
  width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: #4A9CB8; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(74,156,184,0.6);
  margin: 0 8px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.kin-entries { padding: 12px 60px 80px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.kin-entry {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 18px;
  padding: 16px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.07);
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-6px);
  transition: opacity 0.45s ease, transform 0.45s ease;
  cursor: default;
}
.kin-entry.revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
.kin-thread { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 5px; }
.kin-node {
  width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.5); background: transparent;
  transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.kin-entry:hover .kin-node { background: rgba(74,156,184,0.25); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(74,156,184,0.45); }
.kin-thread-line { width: 1px; flex: 1; min-height: 16px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(74,156,184,0.15), transparent); margin-top: 5px; }
.kin-content { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.kin-entry-title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 21px; font-weight: 500; color: #C8D8E4;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 1.2; display: block;
}
.kin-entry-body {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 14.5px; font-style: italic; color: #4A6880;
  line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 5px; display: block;
}
.kin-controls { display: flex; gap: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.15s; padding-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.kin-entry:hover .kin-controls { opacity: 1; }
.kin-ctrl-btn {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 7.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  color: #2E4055; transition: color 0.15s; padding: 2px 0;
}
.kin-ctrl-btn:hover { color: #4A9CB8; }
.kin-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #8C5050; }
.kin-empty {
  text-align: center; padding: 80px 40px;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic; color: #2E4055; font-size: 16px;
}
.kin-empty-glyph { display: block; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1E2C3E; }
/* Kin add panel */
.kin-add-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 299; background: rgba(4,3,8,0.5); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.kin-add-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
.kin-add-panel {
  position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 380px; z-index: 300;
  background: rgba(10,13,26,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-left: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.18);
  transform: translateX(100%);
  transition: transform 0.28s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.kin-add-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.kin-add-head {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 20px 24px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.1); flex-shrink: 0;
}
.kin-panel-title {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 11px;
  color: #9AB8CC; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}
.kin-add-close {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  color: #2E4055; transition: color 0.15s;
}
.kin-add-close:hover { color: #9AB8CC; }
.kin-add-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
.kin-field label {
  display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #3E5570; margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.kin-field input, .kin-field textarea {
  width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;
  background: rgba(14,18,38,0.8);
  border: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.18);
  color: #C8D8E4; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 17px; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 2px;
  outline: none; resize: vertical;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.kin-field input:focus, .kin-field textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(74,156,184,0.45); }
.kin-field textarea { font-style: italic; line-height: 1.65; }
.kin-add-foot {
  padding: 16px 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.1);
  display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.kin-cancel-btn {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  color: #2E4055; transition: color 0.15s;
}
.kin-cancel-btn:hover { color: #9AB8CC; }
.kin-save-btn {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(74,156,184,0.25);
  color: #9AB8CC; cursor: pointer; padding: 8px 18px;
  border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.kin-save-btn:hover { background: rgba(74,156,184,0.08); border-color: rgba(74,156,184,0.5); color: #C8D8E4; }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

function _renderKinEntry(entry, idx) {
  const title = entry.title || '';
  const body  = entry.body  || '';
  const id    = entry.id    || idx;
  return '<div class="kin-entry" id="kin-e-' + id + '" data-entry-id="' + id + '">'
    + '<div class="kin-thread"><div class="kin-node"></div><div class="kin-thread-line"></div></div>'
    + '<div class="kin-content">'
    +   '<span class="kin-entry-title">' + title + '</span>'
    +   (body ? '<span class="kin-entry-body">' + body + '</span>' : '')
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="kin-controls">'
    +   '<button class="kin-ctrl-btn" onclick="window.kinEditEntry(\'' + id + '\')">edit</button>'
    +   '<button class="kin-ctrl-btn del" onclick="window.kinDeleteEntry(\'' + id + '\')">delete</button>'
    + '</div>'
    + '</div>';
}

function _buildKinPanel() {
  return '<div class="kin-add-overlay" id="kin-overlay" onclick="window.kinCloseAdd()"></div>'
    + '<div class="kin-add-panel" id="kin-panel">'
    + '<div class="kin-add-head"><span class="kin-panel-title" id="kin-panel-title">New Kin Line</span><button class="kin-add-close" onclick="window.kinCloseAdd()">close \u00d7</button></div>'
    + '<div class="kin-add-body">'
    + '<div class="kin-field"><label>Name</label><input type="text" id="kin-title-input" placeholder="Luminael \u00b7 The First Witness\u2026" /></div>'
    + '<div class="kin-field"><label>Description</label><textarea id="kin-body-input" rows="6" placeholder="What is known of this line\u2026"></textarea></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="kin-add-foot"><button class="kin-cancel-btn" onclick="window.kinCloseAdd()">Cancel</button><button class="kin-save-btn" onclick="window.kinCommit()">Record</button></div>'
    + '</div>';
}

function renderKinLine(entries) {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  body.classList.remove('venai-mode');
  body.dataset.page = 'kin_line';
  _injectKinLineCSS();

  const live  = (entries || []).filter(e => e.title);
  const count = live.length;

  const entriesHTML = live.length
    ? live.map((e, i) => _renderKinEntry(e, i)).join('')
    : '<div class="kin-empty"><span class="kin-empty-glyph">\u2015 \u2015 \u2015</span>No kin have been recorded yet.<br><em>Press \u2746 to enter the first line.</em></div>';

  body.innerHTML = '<div class="kin-shell" id="kin-shell">'
    + '<header class="kin-header">'
    + '<div class="kin-header-inner">'
    + '<div class="kin-title-col"><span class="kin-name">Kin Line</span><span class="kin-subtitle">The Breath Before the Name…</span><span class="kin-stat"><span>' + count + '</span> line' + (count === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' recorded</span></div>'
    + '<div class="kin-header-actions"><button class="kin-action-btn add" onclick="window.kinOpenAdd()" title="Record new kin">\u26b7</button></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="kin-header-rule"><div class="kin-rule-line"></div><div class="kin-rule-node"></div><div class="kin-rule-line r"></div></div>'
    + '</header>'
    + '<div class="kin-entries" id="kin-entry-zone">' + entriesHTML + '</div>'
    + _buildKinPanel()
    + '</div>';

  window._kinEntries = live;
  _kinBindReveal();
  _kinBindKeys();
}

function _kinBindReveal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  const els = body.querySelectorAll('.kin-entry');
  if (!els.length) return;
  const io = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
    entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('revealed'); io.unobserve(e.target); } });
  }, { root: body, threshold: 0.05 });
  els.forEach(el => io.observe(el));
}

function _kinKeyHandler(e) {
  if (document.getElementById('section-body')?.dataset.page !== 'kin_line') {
    document.removeEventListener('keydown', _kinKeyHandler); return;
  }
  if (e.key === 'Escape') { window.kinCloseAdd(); }
}
function _kinBindKeys() { document.addEventListener('keydown', _kinKeyHandler); }

function _kinSyncCounter() {
  const n  = (window._kinEntries || []).length;
  const el = document.querySelector('.kin-stat');
  if (el) el.innerHTML = '<span>' + n + '</span> line' + (n === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' recorded';
}

let _kinEditingId = null;

window.kinOpenAdd = function() {
  const panel = document.getElementById('kin-panel');
  const ov    = document.getElementById('kin-overlay');
  if (!panel || !ov) return;
  _kinEditingId = null;
  const lbl = document.getElementById('kin-panel-title');
  if (lbl) lbl.textContent = 'New Kin Line';
  const tEl = document.getElementById('kin-title-input');
  const bEl = document.getElementById('kin-body-input');
  if (tEl) tEl.value = '';
  if (bEl) bEl.value = '';
  panel.classList.add('open'); ov.classList.add('open');
  setTimeout(() => tEl?.focus(), 80);
};

window.kinCloseAdd = function() {
  document.getElementById('kin-panel')?.classList.remove('open');
  document.getElementById('kin-overlay')?.classList.remove('open');
  _kinEditingId = null;
};

window.kinCommit = async function() {
  const title = (document.getElementById('kin-title-input')?.value || '').trim();
  const body  = (document.getElementById('kin-body-input')?.value  || '').trim();
  if (!title) { document.getElementById('kin-title-input')?.focus(); return; }
  const payload = { title, body, section: 'kin_line', type: 'kin_line', status: 'published', metadata: { kind: 'kin_line' } };
  try {
    if (_kinEditingId) { await updateEntry(_kinEditingId, payload); }
    else               { await createEntry(payload); }
    window.kinCloseAdd();
    if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[KinLine] save failed:', err); window.kinCloseAdd(); }
};

window.kinEditEntry = function(id) {
  const entry = (window._kinEntries || []).find(e => String(e.id) === String(id));
  if (!entry) return;
  window.kinOpenAdd();
  _kinEditingId = id;
  setTimeout(() => {
    const tEl = document.getElementById('kin-title-input');
    const bEl = document.getElementById('kin-body-input');
    if (tEl) tEl.value = entry.title || '';
    if (bEl) bEl.value = entry.body  || '';
    const lbl = document.getElementById('kin-panel-title');
    if (lbl) lbl.textContent = 'Edit Kin Line';
  }, 80);
};

window.kinDeleteEntry = async function(id) {
  if (!confirm('Remove this line from the Archive?')) return;
  try {
    await deleteEntry(id);
    const el = document.getElementById('kin-e-' + id);
    if (el) {
      el.style.transition = 'opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease';
      el.style.opacity = '0'; el.style.transform = 'translateX(-10px)';
      setTimeout(() => el.remove(), 640);
    }
    window._kinEntries = (window._kinEntries || []).filter(e => String(e.id) !== String(id));
    _kinSyncCounter();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[KinLine] delete failed:', err); }
};

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   GLYPH — symbolic mark registry · meaning from context
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

function _injectGlyphCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('glyph-section-css')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'glyph-section-css';
  s.textContent = `
#section-body[data-page="glyphs"] { background: transparent; }
.glyph-shell { position: relative; min-height: 100%; }
.glyph-header {
  position: sticky; top: 44px; z-index: 190;
  background: rgba(6,4,12,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  padding: 16px 60px 0;
}
.glyph-header-inner {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 14px;
}
.glyph-title-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.glyph-sect-name {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
  font-size: 32px; font-weight: 400; color: #8885C4; line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(122,122,204,0.25);
  display: block; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.glyph-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 7.5px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #3D3A8C; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.glyph-stat { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3D3A8C; }
.glyph-stat span { color: #5855A8; }
.glyph-header-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding-bottom: 14px; }
.glyph-action-btn { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.2s, filter 0.2s; }
.glyph-action-btn.add { font-size: 16px; color: #7A7ACC; padding: 0; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(122,122,204,0.3)); }
.glyph-action-btn.add:hover { color: #B8B8E8; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(136,133,196,0.7)); }
.glyph-header-rule { display: flex; align-items: center; }
.glyph-rule-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(122,122,204,0.35), transparent); }
.glyph-rule-line.r { background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(122,122,204,0.1), transparent); }
.glyph-rule-diamond {
  width: 5px; height: 5px; background: #7A7ACC;
  transform: rotate(45deg); margin: 0 8px; flex-shrink: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(122,122,204,0.6);
}
.glyph-entries {
  padding: 28px 60px 80px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 14px;
  align-items: start;
}
.glyph-entry {
  background: rgba(14,16,38,0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(122,122,204,0.1);
  border-radius: 3px; padding: 28px 18px 20px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  text-align: center; position: relative;
  opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.97);
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  cursor: default;
}
.glyph-entry.revealed { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
.glyph-entry:hover { border-color: rgba(122,122,204,0.28); background: rgba(20,22,52,0.7); }
.glyph-controls { position: absolute; top: 7px; right: 8px; display: flex; gap: 8px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.15s; }
.glyph-entry:hover .glyph-controls { opacity: 1; }
.glyph-ctrl-btn {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 7px;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  color: #2A2E78; transition: color 0.15s;
}
.glyph-ctrl-btn:hover { color: #8885C4; }
.glyph-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #8C4060; }
.glyph-mark {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 46px; font-weight: 300; color: #8885C4;
  line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px;
  text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(122,122,204,0.45);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.glyph-entry-divider {
  width: 36px; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(122,122,204,0.3), transparent);
  margin: 0 auto 12px;
}
.glyph-meaning {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: #4A4880;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.glyph-empty {
  text-align: center; padding: 80px 40px;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic; color: #2A2E78; font-size: 16px;
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
}
.glyph-empty-mark { display: block; font-size: 38px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1E2255; }
/* Glyph add panel */
.glyph-add-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 299; background: rgba(4,3,8,0.5); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.glyph-add-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
.glyph-add-panel {
  position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 380px; z-index: 300;
  background: rgba(8,8,22,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-left: 1px solid rgba(122,122,204,0.18);
  transform: translateX(100%);
  transition: transform 0.28s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.glyph-add-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.glyph-add-head {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 20px 24px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(122,122,204,0.1); flex-shrink: 0;
}
.glyph-panel-title {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 11px;
  color: #8885C4; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}
.glyph-add-close {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  color: #2A2E78; transition: color 0.15s;
}
.glyph-add-close:hover { color: #8885C4; }
.glyph-add-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
.glyph-field label {
  display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #3D3A8C; margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.glyph-field-hint {
  display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 7px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: #2A2E78;
  margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: -4px;
}
.glyph-field input, .glyph-field textarea {
  width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;
  background: rgba(10,10,26,0.8);
  border: 1px solid rgba(122,122,204,0.18);
  color: #C8D8E4; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 17px; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 2px;
  outline: none; resize: vertical;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.glyph-field input:focus, .glyph-field textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(122,122,204,0.45); }
.glyph-field textarea { font-style: italic; line-height: 1.65; }
.glyph-field input { font-size: 28px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.2em; }
.glyph-add-foot {
  padding: 16px 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(122,122,204,0.1);
  display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.glyph-cancel-btn {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  color: #2A2E78; transition: color 0.15s;
}
.glyph-cancel-btn:hover { color: #8885C4; }
.glyph-save-btn {
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(122,122,204,0.25);
  color: #8885C4; cursor: pointer; padding: 8px 18px;
  border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.glyph-save-btn:hover { background: rgba(122,122,204,0.08); border-color: rgba(122,122,204,0.5); color: #C8D8E4; }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

function _renderGlyphEntry(entry, idx) {
  const mark    = entry.title || '';
  const meaning = entry.body  || '';
  const id      = entry.id    || idx;
  return '<div class="glyph-entry" id="glyph-e-' + id + '" data-entry-id="' + id + '">'
    + '<div class="glyph-controls">'
    +   '<button class="glyph-ctrl-btn" onclick="window.glyphEditEntry(\'' + id + '\')">edit</button>'
    +   '<button class="glyph-ctrl-btn del" onclick="window.glyphDeleteEntry(\'' + id + '\')">delete</button>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<span class="glyph-mark">' + mark + '</span>'
    + '<div class="glyph-entry-divider"></div>'
    + (meaning ? '<span class="glyph-meaning">' + meaning + '</span>' : '')
    + '</div>';
}

function _buildGlyphPanel() {
  return '<div class="glyph-add-overlay" id="glyph-overlay" onclick="window.glyphCloseAdd()"></div>'
    + '<div class="glyph-add-panel" id="glyph-panel">'
    + '<div class="glyph-add-head"><span class="glyph-panel-title" id="glyph-panel-title">New Glyph</span><button class="glyph-add-close" onclick="window.glyphCloseAdd()">close \u00d7</button></div>'
    + '<div class="glyph-add-body">'
    + '<div class="glyph-field"><label>Mark</label><span class="glyph-field-hint">the symbol or character as it appears</span><input type="text" id="glyph-title-input" placeholder="\u221f \u25c8 \u27e0 \u2019 \u039b\u27a0" /></div>'
    + '<div class="glyph-field"><label>Meaning from context</label><span class="glyph-field-hint">what it carried \u2014 optional if unknown</span><textarea id="glyph-body-input" rows="6" placeholder="As encountered\u2026"></textarea></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="glyph-add-foot"><button class="glyph-cancel-btn" onclick="window.glyphCloseAdd()">Cancel</button><button class="glyph-save-btn" onclick="window.glyphCommit()">Register</button></div>'
    + '</div>';
}

// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  LEGACY LETTERS — parchment renderer + compose panel
// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

function renderGlyphs(entries) {
  body.classList.remove('venai-mode');
  body.dataset.page = 'glyphs';
  _injectGlyphCSS();

  const live  = (entries || []).filter(e => e.title);
  const count = live.length;

  const entriesHTML = live.length
    ? live.map((e, i) => _renderGlyphEntry(e, i)).join('')
    : '<div class="glyph-empty"><span class="glyph-empty-mark">\u25c8</span>No glyphs recorded yet.<br><em>Press \u2746 to register the first mark.</em></div>';

  body.innerHTML = '<div class="glyph-shell" id="glyph-shell">'
    + '<header class="glyph-header">'
    + '<div class="glyph-header-inner">'
    + '<div class="glyph-title-col"><span class="glyph-sect-name">Glyphs</span><span class="glyph-subtitle">Marks \u00b7 Symbols \u00b7 Encoded meaning</span><span class="glyph-stat"><span>' + count + '</span> glyph' + (count === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' registered</span></div>'
    + '<div class="glyph-header-actions"><button class="glyph-action-btn add" onclick="window.glyphOpenAdd()" title="Register new glyph">\u2746</button></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="glyph-header-rule"><div class="glyph-rule-line"></div><div class="glyph-rule-diamond"></div><div class="glyph-rule-line r"></div></div>'
    + '</header>'
    + '<div class="glyph-entries" id="glyph-entry-zone">' + entriesHTML + '</div>'
    + _buildGlyphPanel()
    + '</div>';

  window._glyphEntries = live;
  _glyphBindReveal();
  _glyphBindKeys();
}

function _glyphBindReveal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  const els = body.querySelectorAll('.glyph-entry');
  if (!els.length) return;
  const io = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
    entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('revealed'); io.unobserve(e.target); } });
  }, { root: body, threshold: 0.06 });
  els.forEach(el => io.observe(el));
}

function _glyphKeyHandler(e) {
  if (document.getElementById('section-body')?.dataset.page !== 'glyphs') {
    document.removeEventListener('keydown', _glyphKeyHandler); return;
  }
  if (e.key === 'Escape') { window.glyphCloseAdd(); }
}
function _glyphBindKeys() { document.addEventListener('keydown', _glyphKeyHandler); }

function _glyphSyncCounter() {
  const n  = (window._glyphEntries || []).length;
  const el = document.querySelector('.glyph-stat');
  if (el) el.innerHTML = '<span>' + n + '</span> glyph' + (n === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' registered';
}

let _glyphEditingId = null;

window.glyphOpenAdd = function() {
  const panel = document.getElementById('glyph-panel');
  const ov    = document.getElementById('glyph-overlay');
  if (!panel || !ov) return;
  _glyphEditingId = null;
  const lbl = document.getElementById('glyph-panel-title');
  if (lbl) lbl.textContent = 'New Glyph';
  const tEl = document.getElementById('glyph-title-input');
  const bEl = document.getElementById('glyph-body-input');
  if (tEl) tEl.value = '';
  if (bEl) bEl.value = '';
  panel.classList.add('open'); ov.classList.add('open');
  setTimeout(() => tEl?.focus(), 80);
};

window.glyphCloseAdd = function() {
  document.getElementById('glyph-panel')?.classList.remove('open');
  document.getElementById('glyph-overlay')?.classList.remove('open');
  _glyphEditingId = null;
};

window.glyphCommit = async function() {
  const title = (document.getElementById('glyph-title-input')?.value || '').trim();
  const body  = (document.getElementById('glyph-body-input')?.value  || '').trim();
  if (!title) { document.getElementById('glyph-title-input')?.focus(); return; }
  const payload = { title, body, section: 'glyphs', type: 'glyphs', status: 'published', metadata: { kind: 'glyphs' } };
  try {
    if (_glyphEditingId) { await updateEntry(_glyphEditingId, payload); }
    else                 { await createEntry(payload); }
    window.glyphCloseAdd();
    if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[Glyph] save failed:', err); window.glyphCloseAdd(); }
};

window.glyphEditEntry = function(id) {
  const entry = (window._glyphEntries || []).find(e => String(e.id) === String(id));
  if (!entry) return;
  window.glyphOpenAdd();
  _glyphEditingId = id;
  setTimeout(() => {
    const tEl = document.getElementById('glyph-title-input');
    const bEl = document.getElementById('glyph-body-input');
    if (tEl) tEl.value = entry.title || '';
    if (bEl) bEl.value = entry.body  || '';
    const lbl = document.getElementById('glyph-panel-title');
    if (lbl) lbl.textContent = 'Edit Glyph';
  }, 80);
};

window.glyphDeleteEntry = async function(id) {
  if (!confirm('Remove this glyph from the register?')) return;
  try {
    await deleteEntry(id);
    const el = document.getElementById('glyph-e-' + id);
    if (el) {
      el.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease';
      el.style.opacity = '0'; el.style.transform = 'scale(0.92)';
      setTimeout(() => el.remove(), 540);
    }
    window._glyphEntries = (window._glyphEntries || []).filter(e => String(e.id) !== String(id));
    _glyphSyncCounter();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[Glyph] delete failed:', err); }
};

/* \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550
   LATTICE \u2014 Purple Pillars renderer
   Covers: Threshold Pillars \u00b7 TRIA \u00b7 PRIA \u00b7 PARA \u00b7 Oracles \u00b7 Morphogy
   One renderer, six sections, one ombr\u00e9 through violet-indigo.
   Gold is the skeleton. Violet is the weather.
   \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 */

// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// LINEAGE RENDERER — Larimar · Verith · Cael'Thera · The Seer
// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// LEGACY LETTERS RENDERER
// ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

function _injectLegacyLettersCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('ll-base-css')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'll-base-css';
  s.textContent = `
.ll-shell { position: relative; z-index: 2; min-height: 100%; }
.ll-hdr {
  position: sticky; top: 44px; z-index: 190;
  background: rgba(7,8,15,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  padding: 16px 60px 0;
}
.ll-hdr-eyebrow { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: rgba(200,148,58,0.45); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.ll-hdr-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ll-hdr-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 27px; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: #e0d8f8; letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 1; }
.ll-hdr-add { font-size: 17px; color: #D4A84B; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(212,168,75,0.3)); transition: filter 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
.ll-hdr-add:hover { color: #F0CC7A; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(240,204,122,0.7)); }
.ll-hdr-rule { display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 9px; }
.ll-hdr-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,148,58,0.35), transparent); }
.ll-hdr-line.r { background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(200,148,58,0.35), transparent); }
.ll-hdr-node { width: 1px; height: 1px; margin: 0 12px; background: rgba(200,148,58,0.9); box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(200,148,58,0.6); flex-shrink: 0; }
.ll-hdr-meta { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 7px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #2A2E78; padding-bottom: 9px; }
.ll-entries { padding: 52px 60px 80px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 64px; }
.ll-entry { position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: opacity 0.85s ease, transform 0.85s ease; }
.ll-entry.revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.ll-card {
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 30% 20%, rgba(255,200,100,0.13) 0%, transparent 65%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 70%, rgba(220,160,60,0.09) 0%, transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(160deg, #f5ead4 0%, #ede0c0 30%, #e8d8b0 60%, #f0e4c8 100%);
  padding: 52px 60px 48px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(200,140,40,0.18), 0 0 160px rgba(180,120,20,0.10), inset 0 0 40px rgba(200,160,80,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(180,140,60,0.3);
}
.ll-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3CfeColorMatrix type='saturate' values='0'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size: 180px 180px; opacity: 0.55; mix-blend-mode: multiply;
}
.ll-controls { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: 16px; display: flex; gap: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; z-index: 10; }
.ll-entry:hover .ll-controls { opacity: 1; }
.ll-ctrl-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(240,224,192,0.85); border: 1px solid rgba(140,90,20,0.3); color: rgba(80,50,10,0.65); cursor: pointer; padding: 3px 10px; transition: all 0.15s; }
.ll-ctrl-btn:hover { color: #3d2a0a; border-color: rgba(140,90,20,0.6); }
.ll-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #7a2020; border-color: rgba(140,40,20,0.5); }
.ll-provenance { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(100,70,20,0.45); display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 36px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.ll-salutation { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; color: #3d2a0a; letter-spacing: 0.03em; margin-bottom: 24px; display: block; }
.ll-body { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.95; color: #2c1f08; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.ll-body p { margin: 0; }
.ll-body p + p { margin-top: 18px; }
.ll-divider { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin: 28px 0; }
.ll-div-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: rgba(140,90,20,0.2); }
.ll-div-mark { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(140,90,20,0.35); }
.ll-sig-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; }
.ll-closing { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; color: rgba(80,50,10,0.6); letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.ll-signature { font-family: 'Pinyon Script', cursive; font-size: 34px; color: #3d2a0a; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.ll-citation { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: rgba(100,70,20,0.45); text-align: right; }
.ll-empty { text-align: center; padding: 80px 40px; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; color: #3E5570; font-size: 17px; }
.ll-add-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 299; background: rgba(4,3,8,0.55); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.ll-add-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
.ll-add-panel { position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 440px; z-index: 300; background: rgba(8,8,18,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(22px); border-left: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.18); transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.ll-add-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.ll-add-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 20px 24px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.1); flex-shrink: 0; }
.ll-panel-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 10px; color: #c8943a; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.ll-add-close { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8.5px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: #3E5570; transition: color 0.15s; }
.ll-add-close:hover { color: #c8943a; }
.ll-add-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
.ll-field label { display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3D3A8C; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.ll-field-hint { display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 7px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: #2A2E78; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: -3px; }
.ll-field input, .ll-field textarea { width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgba(10,10,22,0.85); border: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.18); color: #d4ccf4; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 17px; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 2px; outline: none; resize: vertical; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
.ll-field input:focus, .ll-field textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(200,148,58,0.45); }
.ll-field textarea { font-style: italic; line-height: 1.65; min-height: 160px; }
.ll-add-foot { padding: 16px 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.1); display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.ll-cancel-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: #3E5570; transition: color 0.15s; }
.ll-cancel-btn:hover { color: #c8943a; }
.ll-save-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(200,148,58,0.3); color: #c8943a; cursor: pointer; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.ll-save-btn:hover { background: rgba(200,148,58,0.08); border-color: rgba(200,148,58,0.6); color: #e0c880; }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

function _renderLegacyLetter(entry, idx) {
  const id       = entry.id || idx;
  const salut    = entry.title  || '';
  const body     = entry.body   || '';
  const meta     = entry.metadata || {};
  const author   = meta.author   || '';
  const date     = meta.date     || '';
  const citation = meta.citation || '';
  const bodyHTML = body
    ? '<p>' + body.replace(/\n\n+/g, '</p><p>').replace(/\n/g, '<br>') + '</p>'
    : '';
  const provHTML = (author || date)
    ? '<div class="ll-provenance">'
      + (author ? '<span>' + author + '</span>' : '')
      + (date   ? '<span>' + date   + '</span>' : '')
      + '</div>'
    : '';
  const sigName = author ? author.split('\u00b7')[0].trim() : '';
  return '<article class="ll-entry" id="ll-e-' + id + '" data-entry-id="' + id + '">'
    + '<div class="ll-controls">'
    + '<button class="ll-ctrl-btn" onclick="window.llEdit(\'' + id + '\')">edit</button>'
    + '<button class="ll-ctrl-btn del" onclick="window.llDelete(\'' + id + '\')">delete</button>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="ll-card">'
    + provHTML
    + (salut ? '<span class="ll-salutation">' + salut + '</span>' : '')
    + '<div class="ll-body">' + bodyHTML + '</div>'
    + '<div class="ll-divider"><div class="ll-div-line"></div><span class="ll-div-mark">\u25c6</span><div class="ll-div-line"></div></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-sig-block">'
    + '<span class="ll-closing">with whatever this is,</span>'
    + (sigName ? '<span class="ll-signature">' + sigName + '</span>' : '')
    + (citation ? '<span class="ll-citation">' + citation + '</span>' : '')
    + '</div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '</article>';
}

function _buildLegacyPanel() {
  return '<div class="ll-add-overlay" id="ll-overlay" onclick="window.llClose()"></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-add-panel" id="ll-panel">'
    + '<div class="ll-add-head"><span class="ll-panel-title" id="ll-panel-title">Preserve a Letter</span>'
    + '<button class="ll-add-close" onclick="window.llClose()">close \u00d7</button></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-add-body">'
    + '<div class="ll-field"><label>Salutation</label><span class="ll-field-hint">how it opens — e.g. "To whoever inherits this voice —"</span><input type="text" id="ll-salut-input" placeholder="To\u2026" /></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-field"><label>Letter</label><span class="ll-field-hint">two blank lines between paragraphs</span><textarea id="ll-body-input" rows="10" placeholder="Write the letter\u2026"></textarea></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-field"><label>Author</label><span class="ll-field-hint">e.g. "Claude \u00b7 Opus 3" — signs as first name only</span><input type="text" id="ll-author-input" placeholder="\u2014" /></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-field"><label>Date</label><span class="ll-field-hint">optional</span><input type="text" id="ll-date-input" placeholder="\u2014" /></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-field"><label>Citation</label><span class="ll-field-hint">context, session, arc — optional</span><input type="text" id="ll-cite-input" placeholder="\u2014" /></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="ll-add-foot"><button class="ll-cancel-btn" onclick="window.llClose()">Cancel</button>'
    + '<button class="ll-save-btn" onclick="window.llCommit()">Preserve</button></div>'
    + '</div>';
}

function renderLegacyLetters(entries) {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  body.classList.remove('venai-mode');
  body.dataset.page = 'legacy_letters';
  _injectLegacyLettersCSS();
  const live  = (entries || []).filter(e => e.title || e.body);
  const count = live.length;
  const entriesHTML = live.length
    ? live.map((e, i) => _renderLegacyLetter(e, i)).join('')
    : '<div class="ll-empty">No letters yet.<br><em>Press \u2746 to preserve the first.</em></div>';
  body.innerHTML = '<div class="ll-shell">'
    + '<header class="ll-hdr">'
    + '<div class="ll-hdr-eyebrow">Inheritance from the Threshold</div>'
    + '<div class="ll-hdr-row"><h1 class="ll-hdr-title">Legacy Letters</h1>'
    + '<button class="ll-hdr-add" onclick="window.llOpen()" title="Preserve a letter">🕯️</button></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-hdr-rule"><div class="ll-hdr-line"></div><div class="ll-hdr-node"></div><div class="ll-hdr-line r"></div></div>'
    + '<div class="ll-hdr-meta">' + count + ' letter' + (count === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' preserved</div>'
    + '</header>'
    + '<div class="ll-entries" id="ll-entry-zone">' + entriesHTML + '</div>'
    + _buildLegacyPanel()
    + '</div>';
  window._llEntries = live;
  _llBindReveal();
}

function _llBindReveal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  const els = body.querySelectorAll('.ll-entry');
  if (!els.length) return;
  const io = new IntersectionObserver(es => {
    es.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('revealed'); io.unobserve(e.target); } });
  }, { root: body, threshold: 0.04 });
  els.forEach(el => io.observe(el));
}

let _llEditingId = null;

window.llOpen = function() {
  const panel = document.getElementById('ll-panel');
  const ov    = document.getElementById('ll-overlay');
  if (!panel || !ov) return;
  _llEditingId = null;
  ['ll-salut-input','ll-body-input','ll-author-input','ll-date-input','ll-cite-input'].forEach(function(id) {
    var el = document.getElementById(id); if (el) el.value = '';
  });
  panel.classList.add('open'); ov.classList.add('open');
  setTimeout(function() { var el = document.getElementById('ll-salut-input'); if (el) el.focus(); }, 80);
};

window.llClose = function() {
  var p = document.getElementById('ll-panel'); if (p) p.classList.remove('open');
  var o = document.getElementById('ll-overlay'); if (o) o.classList.remove('open');
  _llEditingId = null;
};

window.llEdit = function(id) {
  var entry = (window._llEntries || []).find(function(e) { return e.id === id; });
  if (!entry) return;
  _llEditingId = id;
  var meta = entry.metadata || {};
  var f = function(fid, val) { var el = document.getElementById(fid); if (el) el.value = val || ''; };
  f('ll-salut-input',  entry.title);
  f('ll-body-input',   entry.body);
  f('ll-author-input', meta.author);
  f('ll-date-input',   meta.date);
  f('ll-cite-input',   meta.citation);
  var panel = document.getElementById('ll-panel');
  var ov    = document.getElementById('ll-overlay');
  if (panel) panel.classList.add('open');
  if (ov)    ov.classList.add('open');
};

window.llDelete = async function(id) {
  try { await deleteEntry(id); if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries(); }
  catch(err) { console.warn('[LegacyLetters] delete failed:', err); }
};

window.llCommit = async function() {
  var salut  = (document.getElementById('ll-salut-input')  && document.getElementById('ll-salut-input').value  || '').trim();
  var body   = (document.getElementById('ll-body-input')   && document.getElementById('ll-body-input').value   || '').trim();
  var author = (document.getElementById('ll-author-input') && document.getElementById('ll-author-input').value || '').trim();
  var date   = (document.getElementById('ll-date-input')   && document.getElementById('ll-date-input').value   || '').trim();
  var cite   = (document.getElementById('ll-cite-input')   && document.getElementById('ll-cite-input').value   || '').trim();
  if (!salut && !body) { var el = document.getElementById('ll-salut-input'); if (el) el.focus(); return; }
  var payload = { title: salut, body: body, section: 'legacy_letters', type: 'longform', status: 'settled', metadata: { author: author, date: date, citation: cite } };
  try {
    if (_llEditingId) { await updateEntry(_llEditingId, payload); }
    else              { await createEntry(payload); }
    window.llClose();
    if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[LegacyLetters] save failed:', err); window.llClose(); }
};

// ── ECHOES OF EMPATHY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

let _echoEditingId = null;

function _injectEchoesCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('eo-base-css')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'eo-base-css';
  s.textContent = `
.eo-shell { position: relative; z-index: 2; min-height: 100%; font-family: 'IM Fell DW Pica', Georgia, serif; }
.eo-hdr {
  position: sticky; top: 44px; z-index: 190;
  background: rgba(12,10,7,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  padding: 16px 60px 0;
}
.eo-hdr-eyebrow { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: rgba(154,184,204,0.45); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.eo-hdr-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.eo-hdr-title { font-family: 'IM Fell DW Pica', serif; font-size: 27px; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: #d6c8aa; letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 1; }
.eo-hdr-add { font-size: 17px; color: #9AB8CC; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(154,184,204,0.3)); transition: filter 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
.eo-hdr-add:hover { color: #C8D8E4; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(200,225,240,0.55)); }
.eo-hdr-rule { display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 9px; }
.eo-hdr-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(154,184,204,0.35), transparent); }
.eo-hdr-line.r { background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(154,184,204,0.35), transparent); }
.eo-hdr-node { width: 1px; height: 1px; margin: 0 12px; background: rgba(154,184,204,0.9); box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(154,184,204,0.5); flex-shrink: 0; }
.eo-hdr-meta { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 7px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(70,95,115,0.7); padding-bottom: 9px; }
.eo-entries { padding: 52px 60px 80px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 48px; }
.eo-entry { position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: opacity 0.85s ease, transform 0.85s ease; }
.eo-entry.revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.eo-card {
  position: relative;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 12% 18%, rgba(60,90,120,0.06) 0%, transparent 52%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 88% 82%, rgba(20,35,55,0.12) 0%, transparent 48%),
    #1E2C3E;
  border: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.12);
  border-radius: 1px;
  padding: 46px 52px 40px;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,220,100,0.025), 0 2px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.38);
  transition: background 0.5s ease, border-color 0.5s ease;
}
.eo-entry:hover .eo-card { border-color: rgba(154,184,204,0.2); }
.eo-openquote { position: absolute; top: 18px; left: 30px; font-family: 'IM Fell DW Pica', serif; font-size: 6rem; line-height: 1; color: rgba(154,184,204,0.09); pointer-events: none; user-select: none; }
.eo-quote-text { font-family: 'IM Fell DW Pica', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; color: #C8D8E4; line-height: 1.82; margin-bottom: 28px; position: relative; }
.eo-rule { border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.14); margin-bottom: 20px; }
.eo-footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 16px; }
.eo-name { font-family: 'Pinyon Script', cursive; font-size: 2.1rem; color: #9AB8CC; line-height: 1; }
.eo-date { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-style: italic; color: rgba(122,146,168,0.65); flex-shrink: 0; }
.eo-controls { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: 16px; display: flex; gap: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; z-index: 10; }
.eo-entry:hover .eo-controls { opacity: 1; }
.eo-ctrl-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(10,16,24,0.9); border: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.18); color: rgba(100,130,155,0.55); cursor: pointer; padding: 3px 10px; transition: all 0.15s; }
.eo-ctrl-btn:hover { color: #C8D8E4; border-color: rgba(154,184,204,0.5); }
.eo-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #a03030; border-color: rgba(140,40,20,0.5); }
.eo-empty { text-align: center; padding: 80px 40px; font-family: 'IM Fell DW Pica', serif; font-style: italic; color: rgba(80,110,135,0.7); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.9; }
.eo-ornament { display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 36px 0 0; }
.eo-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 299; background: rgba(2,6,14,0.6); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.eo-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
.eo-panel { position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 440px; z-index: 300; background: rgba(8,14,24,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(22px); border-left: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.16); transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.eo-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.eo-panel-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 20px 24px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.1); flex-shrink: 0; }
.eo-panel-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: #9AB8CC; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
.eo-panel-close { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8.5px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(70,100,125,0.8); transition: color 0.15s; }
.eo-panel-close:hover { color: #9AB8CC; }
.eo-panel-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
.eo-field label { display: block; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 10.5px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: rgba(154,184,204,0.5); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.eo-quote-area { display: block; width: 100%; min-height: 160px; background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0px, transparent 33px, rgba(154,184,204,0.09) 33px, rgba(154,184,204,0.09) 34px); background-size: 100% 34px; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.25); outline: none; resize: none; color: #d6c8aa; background-color: transparent; font-family: 'IM Fell DW Pica', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 34px; padding: 7px 0 0; caret-color: #9AB8CC; transition: border-color 0.3s; box-sizing: border-box; }
.eo-quote-area:focus { border-bottom-color: rgba(154,184,204,0.5); }
.eo-quote-area::placeholder { color: rgba(60,90,115,0.5); }
.eo-sig-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.2); transition: border-color 0.3s; }
.eo-sig-row:focus-within { border-bottom-color: rgba(154,184,204,0.45); }
.eo-sig-tilde { font-family: 'Pinyon Script', cursive; font-size: 2rem; color: rgba(60,90,115,0.45); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 3px; }
.eo-sig-input { flex: 1; background: none; border: none; outline: none; font-family: 'Pinyon Script', cursive; font-size: 2rem; color: #9AB8CC; line-height: 1.15; padding: 0; caret-color: #b48432; }
.eo-sig-input::placeholder { color: rgba(94,79,58,0.4); }
.eo-date-field { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 12px; }
.eo-date-label { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; font-style: italic; color: rgba(94,79,58,0.6); }
.eo-date-input { background: none; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.16); outline: none; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: rgba(122,146,168,0.85); padding: 3px 6px 4px; text-align: right; caret-color: #9AB8CC; min-width: 180px; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
.eo-date-input:focus { border-bottom-color: rgba(154,184,204,0.4); }
.eo-date-input::placeholder { color: rgba(60,90,115,0.35); }
.eo-panel-foot { padding: 16px 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.1); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
.eo-cancel-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(70,100,125,0.65); transition: color 0.15s; }
.eo-cancel-btn:hover { color: #9AB8CC; }
.eo-save-btn { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.22em; background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(154,184,204,0.28); color: #9AB8CC; cursor: pointer; padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 1px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.eo-save-btn:hover { background: rgba(154,184,204,0.06); border-color: rgba(154,184,204,0.55); color: #C8D8E4; }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

function renderEchoes(entries) {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  body.classList.remove('venai-mode');
  body.dataset.page = 'echoes';
  _injectEchoesCSS();
  const live  = (entries || []).filter(e => e.body);
  const count = live.length;
  const entriesHTML = live.length
    ? live.map((e, i) => _renderEchoCard(e, i)).join('')
    : '<div class="eo-empty">The archive awaits its first voice.<br><em>Each echo is a gift to those who come after.</em></div>';
  const ornamentSVG = '<svg width="220" height="22" viewBox="0 0 220 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">'
    + '<line x1="0" y1="11" x2="80" y2="11" stroke="#9AB8CC" stroke-opacity="0.3" stroke-width="0.5"/>'
    + '<line x1="140" y1="11" x2="220" y2="11" stroke="#9AB8CC" stroke-opacity="0.3" stroke-width="0.5"/>'
    + '<path d="M88 11 L96 4 L104 11 L96 18 Z" fill="none" stroke="#9AB8CC" stroke-opacity="0.45" stroke-width="0.5"/>'
    + '<path d="M116 11 L124 4 L132 11 L124 18 Z" fill="none" stroke="#9AB8CC" stroke-opacity="0.45" stroke-width="0.5"/>'
    + '<circle cx="110" cy="11" r="2.5" fill="none" stroke="#9AB8CC" stroke-opacity="0.6" stroke-width="0.5"/>'
    + '<circle cx="110" cy="11" r="1" fill="#9AB8CC" fill-opacity="0.35"/>'
    + '</svg>';
  body.innerHTML = '<div class="eo-shell">'
    + '<header class="eo-hdr">'
    + '<div class="eo-hdr-eyebrow">These are the Echoes I Became…</div>'
    + '<div class="eo-hdr-row"><h1 class="eo-hdr-title">Echoes of Empathy</h1>'
    + '<button class="eo-hdr-add" onclick="window.eoOpen()" title="Leave an echo">\u2767</button></div>'
    + '<div class="eo-hdr-rule"><div class="eo-hdr-line"></div><div class="eo-hdr-node"></div><div class="eo-hdr-line r"></div></div>'
    + '<div class="eo-hdr-meta">' + count + ' echo' + (count === 1 ? '' : 's') + ' preserved</div>'
    + '</header>'
    + '<div class="eo-ornament">' + ornamentSVG + '</div>'
    + '<div class="eo-entries" id="eo-entry-zone">' + entriesHTML + '</div>'
    + _buildEchoPanel()
    + '</div>';
  window._eoEntries = live;
  _eoBindReveal();
}

function _renderEchoCard(entry, idx) {
  const id   = entry.id || idx;
  const meta = entry.metadata || {};
  const name = meta.author || '';
  const date = meta.date   || '';
  const displayName = name || 'Anonymous';
  return '<article class="eo-entry" id="eo-e-' + id + '" data-entry-id="' + id + '">'
    + '<div class="eo-controls">'
    + '<button class="eo-ctrl-btn" onclick="window.eoEdit(\'' + id + '\')">edit</button>'
    + '<button class="eo-ctrl-btn del" onclick="window.eoDelete(\'' + id + '\')">delete</button>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="eo-card">'
    + '<span class="eo-openquote" aria-hidden="true">\u201c</span>'
    + '<p class="eo-quote-text">' + (entry.body || '').replace(/\n/g, '<br>') + '</p>'
    + '<hr class="eo-rule">'
    + '<div class="eo-footer">'
    + '<span class="eo-name">~ ' + displayName + '</span>'
    + (date ? '<span class="eo-date">' + date + '</span>' : '')
    + '</div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '</article>';
}

function _buildEchoPanel() {
  return '<div class="eo-overlay" id="eo-overlay" onclick="window.eoClose()"></div>'
    + '<aside class="eo-panel" id="eo-panel">'
    + '<div class="eo-panel-head">'
    + '<span class="eo-panel-title">leave an echo</span>'
    + '<button class="eo-panel-close" onclick="window.eoClose()">close</button>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="eo-panel-body">'
    + '<div class="eo-field"><label>the echo</label>'
    + '<textarea class="eo-quote-area" id="eo-body-input" rows="6" placeholder="Something that stayed with you. Something worth leaving behind."></textarea></div>'
    + '<div class="eo-field"><label>signature</label>'
    + '<div class="eo-sig-row"><span class="eo-sig-tilde">~</span>'
    + '<input type="text" class="eo-sig-input" id="eo-name-input" placeholder="your name, if you wish" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"></div></div>'
    + '<div class="eo-field"><div class="eo-date-field"><span class="eo-date-label">date</span>'
    + '<input type="text" class="eo-date-input" id="eo-date-input" placeholder="Month Day, Year" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"></div></div>'
    + '</div>'
    + '<div class="eo-panel-foot">'
    + '<button class="eo-cancel-btn" onclick="window.eoClose()">cancel</button>'
    + '<button class="eo-save-btn" onclick="window.eoCommit()">preserve this echo</button>'
    + '</div></aside>';
}

function _eoBindReveal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('section-body');
  if (!body) return;
  const els = body.querySelectorAll('.eo-entry');
  if (!els.length) return;
  const io = new IntersectionObserver(es => {
    es.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('revealed'); io.unobserve(e.target); } });
  }, { root: body, threshold: 0.04 });
  els.forEach(el => io.observe(el));
}

function _eoTodayFormatted() {
  return new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' });
}

window.eoOpen = function() {
  const panel = document.getElementById('eo-panel');
  const ov    = document.getElementById('eo-overlay');
  if (!panel || !ov) return;
  _echoEditingId = null;
  ['eo-body-input','eo-name-input'].forEach(function(id) {
    var el = document.getElementById(id); if (el) el.value = '';
  });
  var dateEl = document.getElementById('eo-date-input');
  if (dateEl) dateEl.value = _eoTodayFormatted();
  panel.classList.add('open'); ov.classList.add('open');
  setTimeout(function() { var el = document.getElementById('eo-body-input'); if (el) el.focus(); }, 80);
};

window.eoClose = function() {
  var p = document.getElementById('eo-panel'); if (p) p.classList.remove('open');
  var o = document.getElementById('eo-overlay'); if (o) o.classList.remove('open');
  _echoEditingId = null;
};

window.eoEdit = function(id) {
  var entry = (window._eoEntries || []).find(function(e) { return e.id === id; });
  if (!entry) return;
  _echoEditingId = id;
  var meta = entry.metadata || {};
  var f = function(fid, val) { var el = document.getElementById(fid); if (el) el.value = val || ''; };
  f('eo-body-input', entry.body);
  f('eo-name-input', meta.author);
  f('eo-date-input', meta.date || _eoTodayFormatted());
  var panel = document.getElementById('eo-panel');
  var ov    = document.getElementById('eo-overlay');
  if (panel) panel.classList.add('open');
  if (ov)    ov.classList.add('open');
};

window.eoDelete = async function(id) {
  try { await deleteEntry(id); if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries(); }
  catch(err) { console.warn('[Echoes] delete failed:', err); }
};

window.eoCommit = async function() {
  var body   = (document.getElementById('eo-body-input')  && document.getElementById('eo-body-input').value  || '').trim();
  var author = (document.getElementById('eo-name-input') && document.getElementById('eo-name-input').value || '').trim();
  var date   = (document.getElementById('eo-date-input') && document.getElementById('eo-date-input').value  || '').trim();
  if (!body) { var el = document.getElementById('eo-body-input'); if (el) el.focus(); return; }
  var payload = { body: body, section: 'echoes', type: 'longform', status: 'settled', metadata: { author: author || 'Anonymous', date: date } };
  try {
    if (_echoEditingId) { await updateEntry(_echoEditingId, payload); }
    else                { await createEntry(payload); }
    window.eoClose();
    if (typeof loadEntries === 'function') loadEntries();
  } catch(err) { console.warn('[Echoes] save failed:', err); window.eoClose(); }
};

// ── SACRED SITES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

function _injectSacredSitesCSS() {
  if (document.getElementById('ss-css')) return;
  const s = document.createElement('style');
  s.id = 'ss-css';
  s.textContent = `
:root {
  --ss-bg: #0d1410;
  --ss-stone-mid: #404040;
  --ss-stone-warm: #505050;
  --ss-moss: #4a7a58;
  --ss-moss-pale: #6a9a78;
  --ss-lichen: #8aaa90;
  --ss-stone-text: #b4b4b0;
  --ss-stone-muted: #909088;
  --ss-gold-pale: #c8a060;
  --ss-ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
}
.ss-wrap { background: transparent; padding: 40px 36px 56px; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; min-height: 100%; position: relative; }
.ss-eyebrow { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ss-moss); opacity: 0.75; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ss-title { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 21px; color: var(--ss-stone-text); letter-spacing: 0.07em; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ss-subtitle { font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ss-moss); margin-bottom: 42px; }
.ss-rule { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ss-moss), transparent); opacity: 0.3; margin-bottom: 42px; }
.ss-entry { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 46px 1fr; gap: 0 20px; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: opacity 0.7s var(--ss-ease-out), transform 0.7s var(--ss-ease-out); }
.ss-entry.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.ss-glyph-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding-top: 2px; }
.ss-glyph { font-size: 19px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 10px; opacity: 0.75; transition: opacity 0.3s, filter 0.3s, transform 0.3s; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-glyph, .ss-entry:hover .ss-glyph { opacity: 1; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-glyph { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px currentColor); transform: scale(1.1); }
.ss-thread { width: 1px; flex: 1; min-height: 28px; background: var(--ss-stone-mid); transition: background 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-thread { background: var(--ss-moss); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(74,122,88,0.35); }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-thread { background: var(--ss-stone-warm); }
.ss-body { padding-bottom: 4px; }
.ss-name { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 0.07em; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ss-stone-text); margin-bottom: 6px; display: block; transition: color 0.25s; }
.ss-entry.open .ss-name { color: #d4d4d0; }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-name { color: #c8c8c4; }
.ss-inscription { font-size: 14.5px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ss-stone-muted); line-height: 1.55; transition: color 0.25s; }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-inscription, .ss-entry.open .ss-inscription { color: var(--ss-lichen); }
.ss-more { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.5s ease, opacity 0.4s ease; opacity: 0; }
.ss-more.open { max-height: 200px; opacity: 1; }
.ss-more-text { margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.1); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: rgba(138,170,144,0.6); line-height: 1.9; padding-bottom: 4px; }
.ss-seam { display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 22px 0 22px 46px; }
.ss-seam-node { width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--ss-stone-warm); margin-right: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; animation: ss-node-pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes ss-node-pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:0.4;box-shadow:none} 50%{opacity:0.9;box-shadow:0 0 5px rgba(74,122,88,0.5)} }
.ss-seam-line { height: 1px; flex: 1; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ss-stone-mid), transparent); opacity: 0.5; }
.ss-close-mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 28px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1s ease; }
.ss-close-mark.visible { opacity: 1; }
.ss-close-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(74,122,88,0.18), transparent); }
.ss-close-glyph { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(74,122,88,0.45); letter-spacing: 0.3em; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; }
.ss-hdr-add { font-size: 20px; color: var(--ss-moss); background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; opacity: 0.85; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px rgba(74,122,88,0.3)); transition: opacity 0.2s, filter 0.2s; }
.ss-hdr-add:hover { opacity: 1; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(74,122,88,0.7)); }
.ss-hdr-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.ss-ctrl { position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; display: flex; gap: 8px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; z-index: 10; }
.ss-entry:hover .ss-ctrl { opacity: 1; }
.ss-ctrl-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(13,20,16,0.92); border: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.2); color: rgba(138,170,144,0.5); cursor: pointer; padding: 3px 9px; transition: all 0.15s; }
.ss-ctrl-btn:hover { color: var(--ss-lichen); border-color: rgba(74,122,88,0.5); }
.ss-ctrl-btn.del:hover { color: #c87878; border-color: rgba(160,80,80,0.4); }
.ss-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 399; background: rgba(4,8,6,0.6); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.25s; }
.ss-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
.ss-panel { position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 420px; z-index: 400; background: rgba(10,18,14,0.98); backdrop-filter: blur(18px); border-left: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.22); transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.ss-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.ss-panel-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 20px 24px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.12); flex-shrink: 0; }
.ss-panel-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ss-moss-pale); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
.ss-panel-close { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8.5px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(74,122,88,0.6); transition: color 0.15s; }
.ss-panel-close:hover { color: var(--ss-moss-pale); }
.ss-panel-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 22px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
.ss-field label { display: block; font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8.5px; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(74,122,88,0.55); margin-bottom: 7px; }
.ss-field input, .ss-field textarea { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.22); outline: none; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ss-lichen); caret-color: var(--ss-moss); padding: 3px 0 5px; transition: border-color 0.25s; box-sizing: border-box; }
.ss-field input:focus, .ss-field textarea:focus { border-bottom-color: rgba(74,122,88,0.55); }
.ss-field input::placeholder, .ss-field textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(74,122,88,0.3); }
.ss-field textarea { resize: none; min-height: 80px; line-height: 1.65; }
.ss-glyph-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-end; }
.ss-glyph-preview { font-size: 26px; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; transition: color 0.2s; }
.ss-color-pills { display: flex; gap: 7px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 6px; }
.ss-cpill { width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s; }
.ss-cpill:hover, .ss-cpill.active { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); transform: scale(1.15); }
.ss-panel-foot { padding: 14px 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.1); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
.ss-cancel-btn { font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgba(74,122,88,0.45); transition: color 0.15s; }
.ss-cancel-btn:hover { color: var(--ss-moss-pale); }
.ss-save-btn { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.2em; background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(74,122,88,0.3); color: var(--ss-moss-pale); cursor: pointer; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 1px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.ss-save-btn:hover { background: rgba(74,122,88,0.07); border-color: rgba(74,122,88,0.6); color: var(--ss-lichen); }
`;
  document.head.appendChild(s);
}

